/-! ### Sub-lemmas for `chebotarev_density`

Decomposed per Sharifi 7.2.2 Step 1 (p. 143). Source quote (verbatim):

> "Let Пғ вҲҲ C and E = L^вҹЁПғвҹ© so that L/E is cyclic of degree f = |вҹЁПғвҹ©|.
> [вҖҰ] Let T_Пғ be the set of primes P of E unramified in L and over K
> with Frobenius ПҶ_P at a prime of L over P equal to Пғ. If P вҲҲ T_Пғ,
> then ПҶ_P = Пғ fixes E, so P has degree one over K. As P is by
> definition inert in L, there are exactly |G|/f primes of L over
> P вҲ© K. As the Frobenius elements of such primes are distributed
> evenly among the elements of the conjugacy class C of Пғ, exactly
> |G|/f|C| of these have Frobenius Пғ. We may then compute the
> Dirichlet density of S: Оҙ(S) = lim_{sвҶ’1+} ОЈ_рқ”ӯвҲҲS Nрқ”ӯ^{-s} / ОЈ_рқ”ӯ
> Nрқ”ӯ^{-s} = (f|C|/|G|) lim_{sвҶ’1+} ОЈ_PвҲҲT_Пғ NP^{-s} / ОЈ_P NP^{-s} =
> (f|C|/|G|) Оҙ(T_Пғ), recalling once again that ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯ^{-s} ~ ОЈ_P
> NP^{-s}. Supposing the theorem for K/E, we have Оҙ(T_Пғ) = 1/f, and
> we therefore obtain Оҙ(S) = |C|/|G|."

Four sub-lemmas:
(i) Cyclic subextension: `E = L^вҹЁПғвҹ©`, `[L:E] = |вҹЁПғвҹ©| = ord(Пғ)`.
(ii) Above-counting: for `рқ”ӯ вҲҲ S`, exactly `|G|/(f|C|)` primes `рқ”“` of
    `рқ“һ L` over `рқ”ӯ` have `Frob_рқ”“ = Пғ`, each "below" a unique `P вҲҲ T_Пғ`.
(iii) Density relation `Оҙ_K(S) = (f|C|/|G|) В· Оҙ_E(T_Пғ)` (uses
    `ОЈ Nрқ”ӯ^{-s} ~ ОЈ NP^{-s}` from Density.lean).
(iv) Apply `chebotarev_abelian` to `L/E` (cyclic): `Оҙ_E(T_Пғ) = 1/f`.
-/

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **API gap вҖ” order of the Frobenius equals the residue degree.** For an unramified
prime `рқ”“` of `рқ“һ L`, the decomposition group `D_рқ”“` is cyclic of order the residue degree
`f = [Оә(рқ”“) : Оә(рқ”ӯ)]`, generated by `Frob_рқ”“`; hence `orderOf Frob_рқ”“ = f`. mathlib has
`Ideal.card_stabilizer_eq_card_inertia_mul_finrank` (`|D_рқ”“| = |I_рқ”“| В· f`) but not that
`Frob_рқ”“` generates `D_рқ”“`, so this leaf is a genuine API gap.

The proof identifies `D_рқ”“` with `Gal(Оә(рқ”“)/Оә(рқ”ӯ))` through `Ideal.Quotient.stabilizerHom`, which
is injective because its kernel is the (trivial, as `рқ”“` is unramified) inertia subgroup
(`Ideal.Quotient.ker_stabilizerHom` + `inertiaGroup_trivial_of_unramified`). Under this map the
residue action `hres` of `Frob_рқ”“ = arithFrobAt` is the finite-field Frobenius
`FiniteField.frobeniusAlgEquivOfAlgebraic` (both raise a class to the `Nрқ”ӯ`-th power:
`IsArithFrobAt.mk_apply` resp. `FiniteField.coe_frobeniusAlgEquivOfAlgebraic`), whose order is the
residue degree by `FiniteField.orderOf_frobeniusAlgEquivOfAlgebraic`. -/
theorem orderOf_frobeniusAt_eq_finrank
    (K L : Type*) [Field K] [NumberField K] [Field L] [NumberField L] [Algebra K L] [IsGalois K L]
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime]
    (h : Ideal.ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) рқ”“ = 1) :
    orderOf (frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ h) = Module.finrank (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := by
  have hPbot : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ := ne_bot_of_ramificationIdx_eq_one K L h
  have hpbot : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := Ideal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot (рқ“һ K) hPbot
  haveI : рқ”“.IsMaximal := вҖ№рқ”“.IsPrimeвҖә.isMaximal hPbot
  haveI : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).IsMaximal :=
    (inferInstance : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime).isMaximal hpbot
  haveI : Finite (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := Ideal.finiteQuotientOfFreeOfNeBot рқ”“ hPbot
  letI : Field (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.Quotient.field _
  letI : Field (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := Ideal.Quotient.field _
  haveI : Finite (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) :=
    Ideal.finiteQuotientOfFreeOfNeBot (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) hpbot
  haveI : Algebra.IsSeparable (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := IsGalois.to_isSeparable
  haveI : Algebra.IsAlgebraic (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := Algebra.IsAlgebraic.of_finite _ _
  letI : Fintype (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := Fintype.ofFinite _
  set gвӮҖ : MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/K) рқ”“ :=
    вҹЁarithFrobAt (рқ“һ K) Gal(L/K) рқ”“,
      IsArithFrobAt.arithFrobAt_mem_stabilizer (рқ“һ K) Gal(L/K) рқ”“вҹ© with hgвӮҖ
  have hres : Ideal.Quotient.stabilizerHom рқ”“ (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) Gal(L/K) gвӮҖ
      = FiniteField.frobeniusAlgEquivOfAlgebraic (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := by
    ext x
    obtain вҹЁb, rflвҹ© := Ideal.Quotient.mk_surjective x
    rw [hgвӮҖ, Ideal.Quotient.stabilizerHom_apply,
      FiniteField.coe_frobeniusAlgEquivOfAlgebraic, вҶҗ Nat.card_eq_fintype_card]
    exact (IsArithFrobAt.arithFrobAt (рқ“һ K) Gal(L/K) рқ”“).mk_apply b
  have hinj : Function.Injective (Ideal.Quotient.stabilizerHom рқ”“ (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) Gal(L/K)) := by
    rw [вҶҗ MonoidHom.ker_eq_bot_iff, Ideal.Quotient.ker_stabilizerHom,
      inertiaGroup_trivial_of_unramified K L рқ”“ h, Subgroup.bot_subgroupOf]
  calc orderOf (frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ h)
      = orderOf gвӮҖ := by rw [hgвӮҖ, Subgroup.orderOf_mk]; rfl
    _ = orderOf (Ideal.Quotient.stabilizerHom рқ”“ (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) Gal(L/K) gвӮҖ) :=
        (orderOf_injective _ hinj gвӮҖ).symm
    _ = orderOf (FiniteField.frobeniusAlgEquivOfAlgebraic
          (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“)) := by rw [hres]
    _ = Module.finrank (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) :=
        FiniteField.orderOf_frobeniusAlgEquivOfAlgebraic _ _

/-- **OrbitвҖ“stabilizer count via the residue degree** (Sharifi 7.2.2 Step 1, p. 143).
The number of primes of `рқ“һ L` above `рқ”ӯ` times the residue degree `[Оә(рқ”“вӮҖ) : Оә(рқ”ӯ)]` of any
prime `рқ”“вӮҖ` above `рқ”ӯ` equals `|Gal(L/K)|`. Discharged by mathlib's
`Ideal.ncard_primesOver_mul_card_inertia_mul_finrank` (orbitвҖ“stabilizer) with trivial
inertia (`Ideal.card_inertia_eq_ramificationIdxIn` + `UnramifiedIn` вҹ№ `e = 1`), after
identifying `{рқ”“ // рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ}` with `рқ”ӯ.primesOver (рқ“һ L)`. -/
theorem card_primesAbove_mul_finrank_eq
    (K L : Type*) [Field K] [NumberField K] [Field L] [NumberField L] [Algebra K L] [IsGalois K L]
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K)) [рқ”ӯ.IsPrime] (hunr : UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ)
    (рқ”“вӮҖ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“вӮҖ.IsPrime] (hlo : рқ”“вӮҖ.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) :
    Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ}
        * Module.finrank (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“вӮҖ) = Nat.card Gal(L/K) := by
  have hpbot : рқ”ӯ вү  вҠҘ := UnramifiedIn.ne_bot K L hunr
  have he : Ideal.ramificationIdx (рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K)) рқ”“вӮҖ = 1 :=
    UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“вӮҖ hlo
  have hP0bot : рқ”“вӮҖ вү  вҠҘ := ne_bot_of_ramificationIdx_eq_one K L he
  have hunder : рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K) = рқ”ӯ := hlo.over.symm
  have hp_under_bot : рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := hunder в–ё hpbot
  haveI : рқ”“вӮҖ.IsMaximal := вҖ№рқ”“вӮҖ.IsPrimeвҖә.isMaximal hP0bot
  haveI : (рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K)).IsMaximal :=
    (inferInstance : (рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime).isMaximal hp_under_bot
  haveI : Finite (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“вӮҖ) := Ideal.finiteQuotientOfFreeOfNeBot рқ”“вӮҖ hP0bot
  haveI : Algebra.IsSeparable (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“вӮҖ) := by
    letI : Field (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.Quotient.field _
    letI : Field (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“вӮҖ) := Ideal.Quotient.field _
    exact IsGalois.to_isSeparable
  have H := Ideal.ncard_primesOver_mul_card_inertia_mul_finrank
    (G := Gal(L/K)) (рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K)) рқ”“вӮҖ
  rw [inertiaGroup_trivial_of_unramified K L рқ”“вӮҖ he, Subgroup.card_bot, mul_one] at H
  have hset : (рқ”“вӮҖ.under (рқ“һ K)).primesOver (рқ“һ L)
      = {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) | рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ} := by
    ext рқ”“
    refine вҹЁfun вҹЁhp, hlo'вҹ© => ?_, fun вҹЁhp, hlo', _вҹ© => ?_вҹ©
    В· haveI := hlo'
      exact вҹЁhp, hunder в–ё hlo', Ideal.ne_bot_of_liesOver_of_ne_bot hp_under_bot рқ”“вҹ©
    В· exact вҹЁhp, hunder в–ё hlo'вҹ©
  rwa [hset, вҶҗ Nat.card_coe_set_eq] at H

/-- The residue degree `[Оә(рқ”“) : Оә(рқ”ӯ)]` at an unramified prime `рқ”“` above `рқ”ӯ`, whose
Frobenius class is `C = [Пғ]`, equals `orderOf Пғ`: `Frob_рқ”“` generates `D_рқ”“` of order `f`
(`orderOf_frobeniusAt_eq_finrank`) and is conjugate to `Пғ`
(`frobeniusClass_eq_mk_frobeniusAt`), so the orders agree. -/
theorem finrank_residue_eq_orderOf
    (K L : Type*) [Field K] [NumberField K] [Field L] [NumberField L] [Algebra K L] [IsGalois K L]
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (C : ConjClasses Gal(L/K)) (hПғ : ConjClasses.mk Пғ = C)
    (рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K)) [рқ”ӯ.IsPrime] (hunr : UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ) (hCfrob : frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = C)
    (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime] (hlo : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) :
    Module.finrank (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) = orderOf Пғ := by
  obtain вҹЁc, hcвҹ© : IsConj
      (frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hlo)) Пғ := by
    rw [вҶҗ ConjClasses.mk_eq_mk_iff_isConj,
      вҶҗ frobeniusClass_eq_mk_frobeniusAt K L рқ”ӯ hunr рқ”“ hlo, hCfrob, hПғ]
  rw [вҶҗ hc.orderOf_eq,
    orderOf_frobeniusAt_eq_finrank K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hlo)]

/-- **OrbitвҖ“stabilizer for the primes above `рқ”ӯ`** (Sharifi 7.2.2 Step 1, p. 143). The
Galois group acts transitively on the primes of `рқ“һ L` above `рқ”ӯ`, with stabiliser the
decomposition group `D_рқ”“`; for an unramified prime `D_рқ”“` is cyclic of order `f = ord Пғ`
(generated by the Frobenius). Hence the number of primes above `рқ”ӯ` times `ord Пғ` is
`|Gal(L/K)|`. -/
theorem card_primesAbove_mul_orderOf_eq
    (K L : Type*) [Field K] [NumberField K] [Field L] [NumberField L] [Algebra K L] [IsGalois K L]
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (C : ConjClasses Gal(L/K)) (_hПғ : ConjClasses.mk Пғ = C)
    (рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K)) [рқ”ӯ.IsPrime] (hunr : UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ)
    (_hCfrob : frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = C) :
    Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ} * orderOf Пғ
      = Nat.card Gal(L/K) := by
  obtain вҹЁрқ”“вӮҖ, hpвӮҖ, hloвӮҖ, _вҹ© := exists_prime_liesOver K L рқ”ӯ (UnramifiedIn.ne_bot K L hunr)
  rw [вҶҗ finrank_residue_eq_orderOf K L Пғ C _hПғ рқ”ӯ hunr _hCfrob рқ”“вӮҖ hloвӮҖ]
  exact card_primesAbove_mul_finrank_eq K L рқ”ӯ hunr рқ”“вӮҖ hloвӮҖ

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **Equipotent Frobenius fibres** (the "distributed evenly" of Sharifi 7.2.2, p. 143).
For `IsConj Пғ Пғ'`, conjugating by the witnessing element is a bijection between the primes
above `рқ”ӯ` with `Frob_рқ”“ = Пғ` and those with `Frob_рқ”“ = Пғ'` (via `frobeniusAt_conj_eq`), so the
two Frobenius fibres have equal cardinality. -/
theorem frobeniusFibre_card_eq_of_isConj
    (K L : Type*) [Field K] [NumberField K] [Field L] [NumberField L] [Algebra K L] [IsGalois K L]
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K)) [рқ”ӯ.IsPrime] (hunr : UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ)
    (Пғ Пғ' : Gal(L/K)) (hc : IsConj Пғ Пғ') :
    Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
        frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) = Пғ}
      = Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
        frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) = Пғ'} := by
  obtain вҹЁc, hcвҹ© := isConj_iff.mp hc
  refine Nat.card_congr (Equiv.subtypeEquiv (MulAction.toPerm c) fun рқ”“ вҶҰ ?_)
  simp only [MulAction.toPerm_apply]
  constructor
  В· rintro вҹЁhp, hP, hne, hfrobвҹ©
    haveI := hp
    haveI := hP
    refine вҹЁinferInstance, inferInstance, ?_, ?_вҹ©
    В· rw [вҶҗ Ideal.smul_bot c]
      exact (MulAction.injective c).ne hne
    В· rw [frobeniusAt_conj_eq K L рқ”“ (c вҖў рқ”“)
        (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) _ c rfl, hfrob, hc]
  В· rintro вҹЁhp, hP, hne, hfrobвҹ©
    haveI := hp
    haveI := hP
    have hsmul : cвҒ»В№ вҖў (c вҖў рқ”“) = рқ”“ := inv_smul_smul c рқ”“
    haveI hp' : рқ”“.IsPrime := hsmul в–ё (inferInstance : (cвҒ»В№ вҖў (c вҖў рқ”“)).IsPrime)
    haveI hP' : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ := hsmul в–ё (inferInstance : (cвҒ»В№ вҖў (c вҖў рқ”“)).LiesOver рқ”ӯ)
    have hne' : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ := by
      rw [вҶҗ hsmul, вҶҗ Ideal.smul_bot cвҒ»В№]
      exact (MulAction.injective cвҒ»В№).ne hne
    refine вҹЁhp', hP', hne', ?_вҹ©
    rw [frobeniusAt_conj_eq K L (c вҖў рқ”“) рқ”“
      (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr (c вҖў рқ”“) hP)
      (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP') cвҒ»В№ hsmul, hfrob, вҶҗ hc]
    group

/-- **Balanced fibre count.** If every prime above `рқ”ӯ` has Frobenius in the class `C = [Пғ]`
and conjugate Frobenius values occur equally often (`hequi`), the total number of primes
above `рқ”ӯ` is `|C|` times the number with `Frob_рқ”“ = Пғ`: partition by the (class-`C`-valued)
Frobenius via `Finset.card_eq_sum_card_fiberwise`, then `Finset.sum_const` using `hequi`. -/
theorem card_primesAbove_eq_card_carrier_mul_frobeniusFibre
    (K L : Type*) [Field K] [NumberField K] [Field L] [NumberField L] [Algebra K L] [IsGalois K L]
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (C : ConjClasses Gal(L/K)) (hПғ : ConjClasses.mk Пғ = C)
    (рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K)) [рқ”ӯ.IsPrime] (hunr : UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ) (hCfrob : frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = C)
    (hequi : вҲҖ Пғ' : Gal(L/K), IsConj Пғ Пғ' вҶ’
      Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
          frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) = Пғ}
        = Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
          frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) = Пғ'}) :
    Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ}
      = Nat.card C.carrier
        * Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
          frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) = Пғ} := by
  classical
  have hpbot : рқ”ӯ вү  вҠҘ := UnramifiedIn.ne_bot K L hunr
  haveI : рқ”ӯ.IsMaximal := вҖ№рқ”ӯ.IsPrimeвҖә.isMaximal hpbot
  haveI : Finite (рқ”ӯ.primesOver (рқ“һ L)) := (IsDedekindDomain.primesOver_finite рқ”ӯ (рқ“һ L)).to_subtype
  haveI : Finite {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ} :=
    Finite.of_injective
      (fun рқ”“ : {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ} =>
        (вҹЁрқ”“.1, рқ”“.2.1, рқ”“.2.2.1вҹ© : рқ”ӯ.primesOver (рқ“һ L)))
      fun _ _ hab => Subtype.ext (by simpa using hab)
  haveI : Fintype C.carrier := Fintype.ofFinite _
  have hmem : вҲҖ (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime] (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ),
      frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) вҲҲ C.carrier := by
    intro рқ”“ _ hP
    rw [ConjClasses.mem_carrier_iff_mk_eq, вҶҗ frobeniusClass_eq_mk_frobeniusAt K L рқ”ӯ hunr рқ”“ hP,
      hCfrob]
  have hconj : вҲҖ g : C.carrier, IsConj Пғ g.1 := by
    rintro вҹЁg, hgвҹ©
    rw [ConjClasses.mem_carrier_iff_mk_eq] at hg
    exact ConjClasses.mk_eq_mk_iff_isConj.mp (hПғ.trans hg.symm)
  let F : {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ} вҶ’ C.carrier := fun рқ”“ =>
    haveI := рқ”“.2.1
    вҹЁfrobeniusAt K L рқ”“.1 (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“.1 рқ”“.2.2.1),
      hmem рқ”“.1 рқ”“.2.2.1вҹ©
  rw [вҶҗ Nat.card_congr (Equiv.sigmaFiberEquiv F), Nat.card_sigma]
  have hfib : вҲҖ g : C.carrier,
      Nat.card {рқ”“ // F рқ”“ = g}
        = Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
            frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) = Пғ} := by
    intro g
    rw [hequi g.1 (hconj g)]
    refine Nat.card_congr вҹЁfun x => вҹЁx.1.1, x.1.2.1, x.1.2.2.1, x.1.2.2.2, ?_вҹ©,
      fun x => вҹЁвҹЁx.1, by obtain вҹЁhp, hP, hne, _вҹ© := x.2; exact вҹЁhp, hP, hneвҹ©вҹ©, ?_вҹ©,
      fun _ => rfl, fun _ => rflвҹ©
    В· exact Subtype.ext_iff.mp x.2
    В· obtain вҹЁ_, _, _, hgвҹ© := x.2; exact Subtype.ext hg
  simp_rw [hfib]
  rw [Finset.sum_const, Finset.card_univ, smul_eq_mul, вҶҗ Nat.card_eq_fintype_card]

/-- **Even distribution of Frobenius over the conjugacy class** (Sharifi 7.2.2 Step 1,
p. 143). The Frobenius elements of the primes above `рқ”ӯ` sweep out the conjugacy class
`C = [Пғ]` evenly, so the number of primes above `рқ”ӯ` with `Frob_рқ”“ = Пғ` times `|C|` equals
the total number of primes above `рқ”ӯ`. -/
theorem count_frobenius_eq_sigma_mul_card_carrier
    (K L : Type*) [Field K] [NumberField K] [Field L] [NumberField L] [Algebra K L] [IsGalois K L]
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (C : ConjClasses Gal(L/K)) (_hПғ : ConjClasses.mk Пғ = C)
    (рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K)) [рқ”ӯ.IsPrime] (hunr : UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ)
    (_hCfrob : frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = C) :
    Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ)
        (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
        frobeniusAt K L рқ”“
            (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP)
          = Пғ}
      * Nat.card C.carrier
      = Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // рқ”“.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ} :=
  (mul_comm _ _).trans (card_primesAbove_eq_card_carrier_mul_frobeniusFibre K L Пғ C _hПғ рқ”ӯ hunr
    _hCfrob fun Пғ' hc вҶҰ frobeniusFibre_card_eq_of_isConj K L рқ”ӯ hunr Пғ Пғ' hc).symm

/-- Sharifi 7.2.2 Step 1, above-counting (p. 143). Verbatim source quote:
"exactly `|G|/f|C|` of these have Frobenius Пғ". For a prime `рқ”ӯ` of
`рқ“һ K` with Frobenius class `C` and a representative `Пғ вҲҲ C`, the count
of primes `рқ”“` of `рқ“һ L` above `рқ”ӯ` with `Frob_рқ”“ = Пғ` is `|G|/(fВ·|C|)`.

This is the substantive new sub-lemma for the conjugacy-class вҶ’
cyclic reduction; the fixed-field cyclic-subextension setup
(`E = L^вҹЁПғвҹ©`, `[L:E] = ord Пғ`) is mathlib's `IntermediateField.fixedField`
and `IsGalois.card_aut_eq_finrank` applied at `вҹЁПғвҹ©`, and the density-lift
formula `Оҙ_K(S) = (f|C|/|G|) Оҙ_E(T_Пғ)` follows from this counting
together with `ОЈ Nрқ”ӯ^{-s} ~ ОЈ NP^{-s}` (Sharifi 7.1.12 applied to both
`K` and `E`). -/
theorem count_primes_above_with_frobenius_eq_sigma
    (K L : Type*) [Field K] [NumberField K] [Field L] [NumberField L] [Algebra K L] [IsGalois K L]
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (C : ConjClasses Gal(L/K)) (_hПғ : ConjClasses.mk Пғ = C)
    (рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K)) [рқ”ӯ.IsPrime] (hunr : UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ)
    (_hCfrob : frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = C) :
    Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ)
        (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
        frobeniusAt K L рқ”“
            (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP)
          = Пғ}
      * orderOf Пғ * Nat.card C.carrier
      = Nat.card Gal(L/K) := by
  rw [mul_right_comm,
    count_frobenius_eq_sigma_mul_card_carrier K L Пғ C _hПғ рқ”ӯ hunr _hCfrob]
  exact card_primesAbove_mul_orderOf_eq K L Пғ C _hПғ рқ”ӯ hunr _hCfrob

omit [IsGalois K L] in
/-- The ratio of the full prime-ideal zeta sums over an intermediate field `E` and
over `K` tends to `1` as `s вҶ“ 1`. Both `ОЈ_univ^{вҶҘE}` and `ОЈ_univ^K` are asymptotic to
`log(1/(s-1))` (`primeIdealZetaSum_univ_tendsto_log`, the `вҶҘE` instance via
`NumberField.of_intermediateField`), so their ratio of ratios cancels. This is the
Lean form of Sharifi's "`ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯ^{-s} ~ ОЈ_P NP^{-s}`" (p. 143). -/
private theorem univ_ratio_E_K_tendsto_one
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (E : IntermediateField K L) :
    Tendsto (fun s : в„қ вҶҰ primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘE))) s
        / primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ K))) s) (рқ“қ[>] 1) (рқ“қ 1) := by
  have hK := primeIdealZetaSum_univ_tendsto_log K
  have hE := primeIdealZetaSum_univ_tendsto_log (вҶҘE)
  have hcancel := hE.div hK one_ne_zero
  rw [one_div_one] at hcancel
  refine hcancel.congr' ?_
  filter_upwards [tendsto_log_one_div_sub_one_atTop.eventually_gt_atTop 0] with s hs
  simp only [Pi.div_apply]
  rw [div_div_div_cancel_rightвӮҖ hs.ne']

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **Frobenius restricts through the tower** (the E-bridge core, Sharifi 7.2.2 p. 143).
For an intermediate field `E` and an unramified prime `рқ”“` of `рқ“һ L` whose residue field over
`рқ“һ вҶҘE` has the same cardinality as over `рқ“һ K` (`hnorm`; the "`рқ”“ вҲ© E` has degree one over
`K`" condition of Sharifi p. 143), the `E`-Frobenius `Frob^E_рқ”“` restricted to `Gal(L/K)`
equals the `K`-Frobenius `Frob^K_рқ”“`.

Both are characterized as raising residue classes to a fixed power
(`IsArithFrobAt`): `Frob^K_рқ”“` to the `N(рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ K)`-th and `Frob^E_рқ”“` to the
`N(рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ вҶҘE)`-th. The restricted automorphism `(Frob^E_рқ”“).restrictScalars K` acts on `рқ“һ L`
exactly as `Frob^E_рқ”“` does (`AlgEquiv.restrictScalars_apply`), so by `hnorm` it raises
residue classes to the `N(рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ K)`-th power too, i.e. it is a `K`-Frobenius at `рқ”“`. The two
`K`-Frobenii then coincide by the uniqueness at an unramified prime
(`IsArithFrobAt.mul_inv_mem_inertia` + trivial inertia, as in `frobeniusAt_conj_eq`).

mathlib has only `isConj_arithFrobAt` (conjugacy of `arithFrobAt` at primes over the same
base); the restriction-through-a-subextension identity is the new tower content. -/
theorem frobeniusAt_restrictScalars_eq [FiniteDimensional K L] (E : IntermediateField K L)
    (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime]
    (hunrK : Ideal.ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) рқ”“ = 1)
    (hunrE : Ideal.ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“ = 1)
    (hnorm : Nat.card (рқ“һ вҶҘE в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) = Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K))) :
    haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘE L := E.isScalarTower_mid'
    (frobeniusAt (вҶҘE) L рқ”“ hunrE).restrictScalars K = frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ hunrK := by
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘE L := E.isScalarTower_mid'
  haveI : IsGalois (вҶҘE) L := IsGalois.tower_top_intermediateField E
  haveI : IsGaloisGroup Gal(L/(вҶҘE)) (вҶҘE) L := IsGaloisGroup.of_isGalois (вҶҘE) L
  haveI hPbot : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ := ne_bot_of_ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK
  haveI : Finite (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := Ideal.finiteQuotientOfFreeOfNeBot рқ”“ hPbot
  change (arithFrobAt (рқ“һ вҶҘE) Gal(L/(вҶҘE)) рқ”“).restrictScalars K = arithFrobAt (рқ“һ K) Gal(L/K) рқ”“
  set ПғE := arithFrobAt (рқ“һ вҶҘE) Gal(L/(вҶҘE)) рқ”“ with hПғE
  set ПғK := arithFrobAt (рқ“һ K) Gal(L/K) рқ”“ with hПғK
  -- `(ПғE).restrictScalars K` is itself a `K`-Frobenius at `рқ”“` (uses `hnorm`).
  have hKfrob1 : IsArithFrobAt (рқ“һ K) (ПғE.restrictScalars K) рқ”“ := by
    have hEfrob : IsArithFrobAt (рқ“һ вҶҘE) ПғE рқ”“ := IsArithFrobAt.arithFrobAt (рқ“һ вҶҘE) Gal(L/(вҶҘE)) рқ”“
    intro x
    have hact : (ПғE.restrictScalars K) вҖў x = ПғE вҖў x := by
      apply Subtype.ext
      change (ПғE.restrictScalars K) вҖў (x : L) = ПғE вҖў (x : L)
      rw [AlgEquiv.smul_def, AlgEquiv.smul_def, AlgEquiv.restrictScalars_apply]
    change (MulSemiringAction.toAlgHom (рқ“һ K) (рқ“һ L) (ПғE.restrictScalars K)) x
      - x ^ Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) вҲҲ рқ”“
    rw [show x ^ Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K))
          = x ^ Nat.card (рқ“һ вҶҘE в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) by rw [hnorm],
      show (MulSemiringAction.toAlgHom (рқ“һ K) (рқ“һ L) (ПғE.restrictScalars K)) x = ПғE вҖў x by
        rw [вҶҗ hact]; rfl]
    exact hEfrob x
  have hKfrob2 : IsArithFrobAt (рқ“һ K) ПғK рқ”“ := IsArithFrobAt.arithFrobAt (рқ“һ K) Gal(L/K) рқ”“
  have hmem := IsArithFrobAt.mul_inv_mem_inertia hKfrob1 hKfrob2
  rw [inertiaGroup_trivial_of_unramified K L рқ”“ hunrK, Subgroup.mem_bot] at hmem
  exact mul_inv_eq_one.mp hmem

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **The decomposition group of `рқ”“` equals `Gal(L/E)`** (Sharifi 7.2.2 p. 143, "`P` is by
definition inert in `L`"). For an unramified `рқ”“` of `рқ“һ L` over `рқ”ӯ = рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ K` whose
`K`-Frobenius is `Пғ`, with `E = L^вҹЁПғвҹ©` and `f = ord Пғ = [L : E]`, the decomposition group
`D_рқ”“ = stab_{Gal(L/K)} рқ”“` is cyclic of order `f` generated by `Frob^K_рқ”“ = Пғ`, hence equals
`вҹЁПғвҹ© = fixingSubgroup E`. Therefore the stabiliser of `рқ”“` inside `Gal(L/E)` is everything:
every `E`-automorphism fixes `рқ”“` (its restriction to `K` lies in `вҹЁПғвҹ© = D_рқ”“`). In particular
`рқ”“` is the unique prime of `рқ“һ L` above `рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E`. -/
private theorem stabilizer_intermediate_eq_top_of_frobenius
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime]
    (hunrK : UnramifiedIn K L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hPK : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hfrob : frobeniusAt K L рқ”“
        (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ hPK) = Пғ)
    (horderE : orderOf Пғ
      = Nat.card Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :
    haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
      (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
    MulAction.stabilizer
        Gal(L/вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) рқ”“ = вҠӨ := by
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
  have hraK := UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ hPK
  have hPbot : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ := ne_bot_of_ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hraK
  have hpbot : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := UnramifiedIn.ne_bot K L hunrK
  haveI : рқ”“.IsMaximal := вҖ№рқ”“.IsPrimeвҖә.isMaximal hPbot
  haveI : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).IsMaximal :=
    (inferInstance : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime).isMaximal hpbot
  haveI : Finite (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := Ideal.finiteQuotientOfFreeOfNeBot рқ”“ hPbot
  haveI : Algebra.IsSeparable (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := by
    letI : Field (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.Quotient.field _
    letI : Field (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := Ideal.Quotient.field _
    exact IsGalois.to_isSeparable
  -- `D_рқ”“ = вҹЁПғвҹ©`: both have order `f` and `Пғ вҲҲ D_рқ”“`.
  have hmem : Пғ вҲҲ MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/K) рқ”“ := by
    rw [вҶҗ hfrob]
    exact (frobeniusAt_spec K L рқ”“ hraK).1
  have hcardstab : Nat.card (MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/K) рқ”“)
      = (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).ramificationIdxIn (рқ“һ L) * (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDegIn (рқ“һ L) :=
    Ideal.card_stabilizer_eq (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) hpbot рқ”“
  have hramIn : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).ramificationIdxIn (рқ“һ L) = 1 := by
    rw [Ideal.ramificationIdxIn_eq_ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) рқ”“ Gal(L/K)]
    exact hraK
  have hdegIn : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDegIn (рқ“һ L)
      = (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg рқ”“ :=
    Ideal.inertiaDegIn_eq_inertiaDeg (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) рқ”“ Gal(L/K)
  have hinertK : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg рқ”“ = orderOf Пғ := by
    rw [Ideal.inertiaDeg_algebraMap, вҶҗ hfrob, orderOf_frobeniusAt_eq_finrank K L рқ”“ hraK]
  have hcardstab' : Nat.card (MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/K) рқ”“) = orderOf Пғ := by
    rw [hcardstab, hramIn, hdegIn, hinertK, one_mul]
  have hstab : Subgroup.zpowers Пғ = MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/K) рқ”“ := by
    refine Subgroup.eq_of_le_of_card_ge (by rw [Subgroup.zpowers_le]; exact hmem) ?_
    rw [Nat.card_zpowers, hcardstab']
  -- transfer to `Gal(L/E)`: every `П„` fixes `рқ”“`.
  rw [eq_top_iff]
  intro П„ _
  rw [MulAction.mem_stabilizer_iff]
  change П„ вҖў рқ”“ = рқ”“
  have hmemfix : П„.restrictScalars K
      вҲҲ IntermediateField.fixingSubgroup (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) :=
    fun x => П„.commutes x
  rw [IntermediateField.fixingSubgroup_fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)] at hmemfix
  have hstabmem : П„.restrictScalars K вҲҲ MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/K) рқ”“ := hstab в–ё hmemfix
  rw [MulAction.mem_stabilizer_iff] at hstabmem
  exact hstabmem

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **The fixed-field prime below `рқ”“` has degree one over `K`** (Sharifi 7.2.2 p. 143, "`P` has
degree one over `K`"). Continuing from `stabilizer_intermediate_eq_top_of_frobenius`: with
`P = рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E`, since `рқ”“` is unramified over `K` the ramification index `e(рқ”“ вҲЈ P) = 1`, and the
decomposition group of `рқ”“` in `Gal(L/E)` being all of `Gal(L/E)` forces the inertia degree
`f(рқ”“ вҲЈ P) = [L : E] = f`, hence by the tower law `f(P вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) = f(рқ”“ вҲЈ рқ”ӯ)/f(рқ”“ вҲЈ P) = f/f = 1`.
The residue field of `P` over `K` is therefore trivial, i.e. `N P = N рқ”ӯ`. -/
private theorem inertiaDeg_under_E_eq_one_of_frobenius
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime]
    (hunrK : UnramifiedIn K L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hPK : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hfrob : frobeniusAt K L рқ”“
        (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ hPK) = Пғ)
    (horderE : orderOf Пғ
      = Nat.card Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :
    haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
      (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
    Ideal.ramificationIdx
        (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) рқ”“ = 1
      вҲ§ (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg
          (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) = 1
      вҲ§ Nat.card (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))
            в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
          = Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := by
  set E := IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ) with hE
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘE L := E.isScalarTower_mid'
  haveI : IsGalois (вҶҘE) L := IsGalois.tower_top_intermediateField _
  have hraK := UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ hPK
  have hPbot : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ := ne_bot_of_ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hraK
  have hpbot : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := UnramifiedIn.ne_bot K L hunrK
  haveI : рқ”“.IsMaximal := вҖ№рқ”“.IsPrimeвҖә.isMaximal hPbot
  haveI : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).IsMaximal :=
    (inferInstance : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime).isMaximal hpbot
  haveI : Finite (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := Ideal.finiteQuotientOfFreeOfNeBot рқ”“ hPbot
  haveI hPEp : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)).IsPrime := inferInstance
  haveI hPK' : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := рқ”“)
  haveI hPEK : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)).LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := inferInstance
  haveI hPPE : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ вҶҘE) (P := рқ”“)
  have hpEbot : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE) вү  вҠҘ := Ideal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot (рқ“һ вҶҘE) hPbot
  haveI : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)).IsMaximal := hPEp.isMaximal hpEbot
  -- `e(рқ”“ вҲЈ P) = 1` from the ramification tower and `e(рқ”“ вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) = 1`.
  have htower : Ideal.ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) рқ”“
      = Ideal.ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE))
        * Ideal.ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“ :=
    Ideal.ramificationIdx_algebra_tower' (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“
  have hraE : Ideal.ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“ = 1 := by
    rw [hraK] at htower
    exact Nat.eq_one_of_mul_eq_one_left htower.symm
  -- `f(рқ”“ вҲЈ P) = [L : E]` from `stabilizer Gal(L/E) рқ”“ = вҠӨ`.
  haveI : Algebra.IsSeparable (рқ“һ вҶҘE в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := by
    letI : Field (рқ“һ вҶҘE в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) := Ideal.Quotient.field _
    letI : Field (рқ“һ L в§ё рқ”“) := Ideal.Quotient.field _
    exact IsGalois.to_isSeparable
  have hstabE : MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/(вҶҘE)) рқ”“ = вҠӨ :=
    stabilizer_intermediate_eq_top_of_frobenius Пғ рқ”“ hunrK hPK hfrob horderE
  have hcardE : Nat.card (MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/(вҶҘE)) рқ”“)
      = (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)).ramificationIdxIn (рқ“һ L) * (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)).inertiaDegIn (рқ“һ L) :=
    Ideal.card_stabilizer_eq (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) hpEbot рқ”“
  rw [hstabE, Subgroup.card_top,
    Ideal.ramificationIdxIn_eq_ramificationIdx (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“ Gal(L/(вҶҘE)), hraE, one_mul,
    Ideal.inertiaDegIn_eq_inertiaDeg (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“ Gal(L/(вҶҘE)),
    Ideal.inertiaDeg_algebraMap] at hcardE
  -- now `[L:E] = f(рқ”“ вҲЈ P)`; combine with `f(рқ”“ вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) = ord Пғ = [L:E]` and the inertia tower.
  have hinertK : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg рқ”“ = orderOf Пғ := by
    rw [Ideal.inertiaDeg_algebraMap, вҶҗ hfrob, orderOf_frobeniusAt_eq_finrank K L рқ”“ hraK]
  have hinertTower : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg рқ”“
      = (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE))
        * (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)).inertiaDeg рқ”“ := by
    rw [Ideal.inertiaDeg_eq_inertiaDeg' (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) рқ”“,
      Ideal.inertiaDeg_eq_inertiaDeg' (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)),
      Ideal.inertiaDeg_eq_inertiaDeg' (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“]
    exact Ideal.inertiaDeg'_tower (R := рқ“һ K) (S := рқ“һ вҶҘE) (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“
  have hfPE : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)).inertiaDeg рқ”“ = orderOf Пғ := by
    rw [Ideal.inertiaDeg_algebraMap, вҶҗ hcardE, horderE]
  have hinertPK : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) = 1 := by
    have hpos : 0 < orderOf Пғ := by rw [orderOf_pos_iff]; exact isOfFinOrder_of_finite Пғ
    rw [hinertK, hfPE] at hinertTower
    -- `orderOf Пғ = f(P вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) * orderOf Пғ`, cancel `orderOf Пғ > 0`.
    refine Nat.eq_of_mul_eq_mul_right hpos ?_
    rw [one_mul]
    exact hinertTower.symm
  refine вҹЁhraE, hinertPK, ?_вҹ©
  -- `N P = N рқ”ӯ` from `f(P вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) = 1`: residue field cardinalities agree.
  have hnormP : Nat.card (рқ“һ вҶҘE в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE))
      = Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) ^ (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) := by
    haveI : Module.Free в„Ө (рқ“һ вҶҘE) := inferInstance
    simpa [Submodule.cardQuot_apply, Ideal.absNorm_apply] using
      (Ideal.absNorm_eq_pow_inertiaDeg_of_liesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K))
        (inferInstance) hpbot)
  rw [hnormP, hinertPK, pow_one]

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **`рқ”“` is the unique prime of `рқ“һ L` above `рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E`** (Sharifi 7.2.2 p. 143, "`P` is by
definition inert in `L`"). Since `stabilizer Gal(L/E) рқ”“ = вҠӨ` and `Gal(L/E)` acts transitively
on the primes above `рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E`, any prime `рқ””` of `рқ“һ L` above `рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E` equals `рқ”“`. -/
private theorem eq_of_liesOver_under_E_of_frobenius
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime]
    (hunrK : UnramifiedIn K L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hPK : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hfrob : frobeniusAt K L рқ”“
        (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ hPK) = Пғ)
    (horderE : orderOf Пғ
      = Nat.card Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (рқ”” : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ””.IsPrime]
    (hQ : haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
        (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
      рқ””.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))) :
    рқ”” = рқ”“ := by
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
  haveI : IsGalois (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L :=
    IsGalois.tower_top_intermediateField _
  haveI : IsGaloisGroup Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
      (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L := IsGaloisGroup.of_isGalois _ L
  set E := IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ) with hE
  haveI := hQ
  haveI : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ вҶҘE) (P := рқ”“)
  have hstabE : MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/(вҶҘE)) рқ”“ = вҠӨ :=
    stabilizer_intermediate_eq_top_of_frobenius Пғ рқ”“ hunrK hPK hfrob horderE
  obtain вҹЁП„, hП„вҹ© := Ideal.exists_smul_eq_of_isGaloisGroup (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘE)) рқ”“ рқ””
    Gal(L/(вҶҘE))
  have hП„mem : П„ вҲҲ MulAction.stabilizer Gal(L/(вҶҘE)) рқ”“ := by rw [hstabE]; exact Subgroup.mem_top П„
  rw [MulAction.mem_stabilizer_iff] at hП„mem
  rw [вҶҗ hП„, hП„mem]

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **The fixed-field Frobenius below `рқ”“` is `Пғ_E`** (Sharifi 7.2.2 p. 143). For an L-prime
`рқ”“` with `Frob^K_рқ”“ = Пғ` lying over a degree-one (over `K`) prime `P = рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E`, the
`E`-Frobenius `Frob^E_рқ”“` restricts to `Пғ`, hence (as `Пғ_E` also restricts to `Пғ` and
`restrictScalars` is injective) `Frob^E_рқ”“ = Пғ_E`. -/
private theorem frobeniusAt_E_eq_of_frobenius
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K))
    (ПғE : Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (hПғE : letI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
        (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
      ПғE.restrictScalars K = Пғ)
    (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime]
    (hunrK : UnramifiedIn K L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hPK : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hfrob : frobeniusAt K L рқ”“
        (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ hPK) = Пғ)
    (horderE : orderOf Пғ
      = Nat.card Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (hraE : Ideal.ramificationIdx
        (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) рқ”“ = 1)
    (hnorm : Nat.card (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))
          в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
        = Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K))) :
    haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
      (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
    frobeniusAt (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L рқ”“ hraE = ПғE := by
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
  haveI : IsGalois (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L :=
    IsGalois.tower_top_intermediateField _
  -- `Frob^E_рқ”“` and `Пғ_E` both restrict to `Пғ`; `restrictScalars` is injective.
  have hbridge := frobeniusAt_restrictScalars_eq
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) рқ”“
    (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ hPK) hraE hnorm
  rw [hfrob] at hbridge
  -- now `(Frob^E_рқ”“).restrictScalars K = Пғ = Пғ_E.restrictScalars K`
  exact AlgEquiv.restrictScalars_injective K (hbridge.trans hПғE.symm)

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **Fibre bijection: degree-one `E`-primes with Frobenius `Пғ_E` вҶ” `L`-primes with
Frobenius `Пғ`** (Sharifi 7.2.2 p. 143). For a prime `рқ”ӯ` of `рқ“һ K` unramified in `L` with
Frobenius class `[Пғ]`, the map `рқ”“ вҶҰ рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E` is a bijection from the primes `рқ”“` of `рқ“һ L`
above `рқ”ӯ` with `Frob^K_рқ”“ = Пғ` onto the primes `P` of `рқ“һ E` above `рқ”ӯ`, unramified in `L`,
with `Frob^E_P = [Пғ_E]` and `f(P вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) = 1`. Hence the two fibres are equinumerous; combined
with the proven count `count_primes_above_with_frobenius_eq_sigma` this gives the number of
such `P` over `рқ”ӯ` as `|G|/(fВ·|C|)`. -/
private theorem card_fibre_E_eq_card_fibre_L
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K))
    (ПғE : Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (hПғE : letI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
        (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
      ПғE.restrictScalars K = Пғ)
    [IsMulCommutative Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))]
    (horderE : orderOf Пғ
      = Nat.card Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K)) [рқ”ӯ.IsPrime] (hunr : UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ)
    (hCfrob : frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = ConjClasses.mk Пғ) :
    haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
      (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
    Nat.card {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) //
        P вҲҲ {P | P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
              вҲ§ frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
                = ConjClasses.mk ПғE
              вҲ§ (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1} вҲ§ P.LiesOver рқ”ӯ вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ}
      = Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
          frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) = Пғ} := by
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
  haveI : IsGalois (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L :=
    IsGalois.tower_top_intermediateField _
  have hpbot : рқ”ӯ вү  вҠҘ := UnramifiedIn.ne_bot K L hunr
  -- `Frob^K_рқ”“ = Пғ` for `рқ”“` over `рқ”ӯ` вҹ№ `ord Пғ = [L:E]` (`horderE` hypothesis) lets the helper
  -- lemmas apply.  Bundle the consequences for the `E`-prime `P = рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E`.
  have hPmem : вҲҖ (рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L)) [рқ”“.IsPrime] (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
      frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunr рқ”“ hP) = Пғ вҶ’
      (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) вҲҲ
          {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
            P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P вҲ§
            frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
              = ConjClasses.mk ПғE вҲ§ (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1}
        вҲ§ (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))).LiesOver рқ”ӯ
        вҲ§ (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) вү  вҠҘ := by
    intro рқ”“ _ hP hPbot hfrob
    haveI := hP
    have hunderK : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K) = рқ”ӯ := hP.over.symm
    have hunrK : UnramifiedIn K L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := hunderK в–ё hunr
    haveI : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := рқ”“)
    have hfrobK : frobeniusAt K L рқ”“
        (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ inferInstance) = Пғ := hfrob
    obtain вҹЁhraE, hinPK, hnormвҹ© :=
      inertiaDeg_under_E_eq_one_of_frobenius Пғ рқ”“ hunrK inferInstance hfrobK horderE
    have hfrE := frobeniusAt_E_eq_of_frobenius Пғ ПғE hПғE рқ”“ hunrK inferInstance hfrobK horderE
      hraE hnorm
    have hunram : UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L
        (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) := by
      refine вҹЁIdeal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot _ hPbot, fun рқ”” hрқ””max hрқ””lo => ?_вҹ©
      haveI := hрқ””max.isPrime
      have hрқ””eq : рқ”” = рқ”“ := eq_of_liesOver_under_E_of_frobenius Пғ рқ”“ hunrK inferInstance hfrobK
        horderE рқ”” hрқ””lo
      subst hрқ””eq
      exact (Algebra.isUnramifiedAt_iff_of_isDedekindDomain hPbot).mpr hraE
    haveI hPEK : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))).LiesOver рқ”ӯ := by
      haveI : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))).LiesOver
          (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := inferInstance
      rw [hunderK] at this; exact this
    haveI hPPE : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :=
      Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) (P := рқ”“)
    have hpEbot : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) вү  вҠҘ :=
      Ideal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot _ hPbot
    refine вҹЁвҹЁinferInstance, hunram, ?_, ?_вҹ©, hPEK, hpEbotвҹ©
    В· -- `frobeniusClass вҶҘE L P = mk ПғE`
      rw [frobeniusClass_eq_mk_frobeniusAt (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))
        L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) hunram рқ”“ hPPE,
        ConjClasses.mk_eq_mk_iff_isConj]
      exact isConj_iff.mpr вҹЁ1, by simp [hfrE]вҹ©
    В· -- `(P.under рқ“һK).inertiaDeg P = 1`
      rw [show (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))).under (рқ“һ K)
          = рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K) from Ideal.under_under рқ”“]
      exact hinPK
  refine (Nat.card_congr (Equiv.ofBijective
      (fun рқ”“ => вҹЁрқ”“.1.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))),
        by obtain вҹЁ_, hP, hPbot, hfrobвҹ© := рқ”“.2; exact hPmem рқ”“.1 hP hPbot hfrobвҹ©)
      вҹЁ?_, ?_вҹ©)).symm
  В· -- injective: `рқ”“вӮҒ вҲ© рқ“һ E = рқ”“вӮӮ вҲ© рқ“һ E` вҹ№ `рқ”“вӮӮ` lies over `рқ”“вӮҒ вҲ© рқ“һ E` вҹ№ `рқ”“вӮӮ = рқ”“вӮҒ`.
    rintro вҹЁрқ”“вӮҒ, hрқ”“вӮҒ, hPвӮҒ, hPвӮҒbot, hfrobвӮҒвҹ© вҹЁрқ”“вӮӮ, hрқ”“вӮӮ, hPвӮӮ, hPвӮӮbot, hfrobвӮӮвҹ© hОҰ
    haveI := hрқ”“вӮҒ; haveI := hрқ”“вӮӮ; haveI := hPвӮҒ; haveI := hPвӮӮ
    have hunderKвӮҒ : рқ”“вӮҒ.under (рқ“һ K) = рқ”ӯ := hPвӮҒ.over.symm
    have hunrKвӮҒ : UnramifiedIn K L (рқ”“вӮҒ.under (рқ“һ K)) := hunderKвӮҒ в–ё hunr
    haveI : рқ”“вӮҒ.LiesOver (рқ”“вӮҒ.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := рқ”“вӮҒ)
    have hfrobKвӮҒ : frobeniusAt K L рқ”“вӮҒ
        (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrKвӮҒ рқ”“вӮҒ inferInstance) = Пғ := hfrobвӮҒ
    have hОҰ' : рқ”“вӮӮ.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))
        = рқ”“вӮҒ.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) :=
      congrArg Subtype.val hОҰ |>.symm
    haveI hPвӮӮlo : рқ”“вӮӮ.LiesOver
        (рқ”“вӮҒ.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) := by
      haveI : рқ”“вӮӮ.LiesOver
        (рқ”“вӮӮ.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :=
        Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) (P := рқ”“вӮӮ)
      rwa [hОҰ'] at this
    exact Subtype.ext (eq_of_liesOver_under_E_of_frobenius Пғ рқ”“вӮҒ hunrKвӮҒ inferInstance hfrobKвӮҒ
      horderE рқ”“вӮӮ hPвӮӮlo).symm
  В· -- surjective: a fibre-prime `P` of `рқ“һ E` has an `L`-prime `рқ”“` above it with `Frob^K_рқ”“ = Пғ`.
    rintro вҹЁP, вҹЁhPp, hPunr, hPfrob, hPdegвҹ©, hPlo, hPbotвҹ©
    haveI := hPp; haveI := hPlo
    obtain вҹЁрқ”“, hрқ”“p, hрқ”“lo, hрқ”“botвҹ© := exists_prime_liesOver
      (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L P hPbot
    haveI := hрқ”“p; haveI := hрқ”“lo
    -- `P = рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E`; transfer `P`'s properties to `рқ”“ вҲ© рқ“һ E`.
    have hPeq : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) = P :=
      hрқ”“lo.over.symm
    haveI hPPE : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :=
      Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) (P := рқ”“)
    have hunderK : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K) = рқ”ӯ := by
      rw [вҶҗ Ideal.under_under (B := рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) рқ”“,
        hPeq]; exact hPlo.over.symm
    haveI hPKрқ”“ : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ := hunderK в–ё Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := рқ”“)
    have hunrK : UnramifiedIn K L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := hunderK в–ё hunr
    haveI : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := рқ”“)
    -- `f(P вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) = 1` (transferred from `hPdeg`).
    have hinertPK1 : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg
        (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) = 1 := by
      rw [hPeq, вҶҗ Ideal.under_under (B := рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))
        рқ”“, hPeq]; exact hPdeg
    -- `e(рқ”“ вҲЈ P) = 1` from `UnramifiedIn вҶҘE L P`; `N P = N рқ”ӯ` from `f(P вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) = 1`.
    have hraE : Ideal.ramificationIdx
        (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) рқ”“ = 1 :=
      (Algebra.isUnramifiedAt_iff_of_isDedekindDomain hрқ”“bot).mp
        (hPunr.2 рқ”“ (hрқ”“p.isMaximal hрқ”“bot) (hPeq в–ё hPPE))
    have hnorm : Nat.card (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))
          в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
        = Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := by
      have hnP : Nat.card (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))
            в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
          = Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K))
            ^ (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg
                (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) := by
        simpa [Submodule.cardQuot_apply, Ideal.absNorm_apply] using
          Ideal.absNorm_eq_pow_inertiaDeg_of_liesOver
            (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K))
            inferInstance (hunderK в–ё hpbot)
      rw [hnP, hinertPK1, pow_one]
    -- `Frob^E_рқ”“ = Пғ_E` (abelian + `frobeniusClass P = mk ПғE`), hence `Frob^K_рқ”“ = Пғ`.
    have hfrEeqПғE : frobeniusAt (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L рқ”“ hraE
        = ПғE := by
      letI : CommMonoid Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :=
        IsMulCommutative.instCommMonoid
      have hcl := frobeniusClass_eq_mk_frobeniusAt
        (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L P hPunr рқ”“ (hPeq в–ё hPPE)
      rw [hPfrob] at hcl
      have hmk : ConjClasses.mk
          (frobeniusAt (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L рқ”“ hraE)
          = ConjClasses.mk ПғE := hcl.symm
      exact isConj_iff_eq.mp (ConjClasses.mk_eq_mk_iff_isConj.mp hmk)
    have hfrobK : frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ inferInstance)
        = Пғ := by
      have hbridge := frobeniusAt_restrictScalars_eq
        (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) рқ”“
        (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ inferInstance) hraE hnorm
      rw [hfrEeqПғE, hПғE] at hbridge
      exact hbridge.symm
    exact вҹЁвҹЁрқ”“, hрқ”“p, hPKрқ”“, hрқ”“bot, hfrobKвҹ©, Subtype.ext hPeqвҹ©

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **A degree-one fibre prime has `K`-Frobenius class `[Пғ]`** (Sharifi 7.2.2 p. 143). If `P`
is a prime of `рқ“һ E` above an unramified-in-`L` prime `рқ”ӯ = P вҲ© рқ“һ K`, unramified in `L`, with
`Frob^E_P = [Пғ_E]` and degree one over `K`, then the `K`-Frobenius class of `рқ”ӯ` is `[Пғ]`. -/
private theorem frobeniusClass_under_eq_of_mem_fibre
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K))
    (ПғE : Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (hПғE : letI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
        (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
      ПғE.restrictScalars K = Пғ)
    [IsMulCommutative Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))]
    (horderE : orderOf Пғ
      = Nat.card Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) [P.IsPrime]
    (hunrP : UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K)))
    (hPunr : UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P)
    (hPfrob : frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
      = ConjClasses.mk ПғE)
    (hPdeg : (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1) (hPbot : P вү  вҠҘ) :
    frobeniusClass K L (P.under (рқ“һ K)) = ConjClasses.mk Пғ := by
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
  haveI : IsGalois (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L :=
    IsGalois.tower_top_intermediateField _
  haveI : (P.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime := inferInstance
  -- pick an `L`-prime `рқ”“` over `P`; show its `K`-Frobenius is `Пғ`.
  obtain вҹЁрқ”“, hрқ”“p, hрқ”“lo, hрқ”“botвҹ© := exists_prime_liesOver
    (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L P hPbot
  haveI := hрқ”“p; haveI := hрқ”“lo
  have hPeq : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) = P :=
    hрқ”“lo.over.symm
  haveI hPPE : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :=
    Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) (P := рқ”“)
  have hunderK : рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K) = P.under (рқ“һ K) := by
    rw [вҶҗ Ideal.under_under (B := рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) рқ”“, hPeq]
  haveI hPKрқ”“ : рқ”“.LiesOver (P.under (рқ“һ K)) := hunderK в–ё Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := рқ”“)
  have hunrK : UnramifiedIn K L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := hunderK в–ё hunrP
  haveI : рқ”“.LiesOver (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := рқ”“)
  -- degree-one вҹ№ `N P = N рқ”ӯ`; `P`-unramified вҹ№ `e(рқ”“ вҲЈ P) = 1`; bridge gives `Frob^K_рқ”“ = Пғ`.
  have hinertPK1 : (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg
      (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) = 1 := by
    rw [hPeq, hunderK]; exact hPdeg
  have hraE : Ideal.ramificationIdx
      (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) рқ”“ = 1 :=
    (Algebra.isUnramifiedAt_iff_of_isDedekindDomain hрқ”“bot).mp
      (hPunr.2 рқ”“ (hрқ”“p.isMaximal hрқ”“bot) (hPeq в–ё hPPE))
  have hnorm : Nat.card (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))
        в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
      = Nat.card (рқ“һ K в§ё рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) := by
    have hnP := Ideal.absNorm_eq_pow_inertiaDeg_of_liesOver
      (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K))
      inferInstance (UnramifiedIn.ne_bot K L hunrK)
    simp only [Submodule.cardQuot_apply, Ideal.absNorm_apply] at hnP вҠў
    rw [hnP, hinertPK1, pow_one]
  have hfrEeqПғE : frobeniusAt (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L рқ”“ hraE
      = ПғE := by
    letI : CommMonoid Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :=
      IsMulCommutative.instCommMonoid
    have hcl := frobeniusClass_eq_mk_frobeniusAt
      (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L P hPunr рқ”“ (hPeq в–ё hPPE)
    rw [hPfrob] at hcl
    exact isConj_iff_eq.mp (ConjClasses.mk_eq_mk_iff_isConj.mp hcl.symm)
  have hfrobK : frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ inferInstance)
      = Пғ := by
    have hbridge := frobeniusAt_restrictScalars_eq
      (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) рқ”“
      (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrK рқ”“ inferInstance) hraE hnorm
    rw [hfrEeqПғE, hПғE] at hbridge
    exact hbridge.symm
  rw [show P.under (рқ“һ K) = рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K) from hunderK.symm,
    frobeniusClass_eq_mk_frobeniusAt K L (рқ”“.under (рқ“һ K)) hunrK рқ”“ inferInstance, hfrobK]

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **LEAF A: the degree-one part of `T` carries the main term** (Sharifi 7.2.2 p. 143). For
`1 < s`, the partial Dirichlet sum over the set `TвӮҒ` of degree-one (over `K`) primes `P` of
`рқ“һ E` above an unramified-in-`L` prime, with `Frob^E_P = [Пғ_E]`, equals `|G|/(fВ·|C|)` times the
partial sum over `S` (the primes of `рқ“һ K` with `K`-Frobenius class `[Пғ]`).  The fibre over
each `рқ”ӯ вҲҲ S` has exactly `|G|/(fВ·|C|)` such primes `P` (the fibre bijection
`card_fibre_E_eq_card_fibre_L` together with the proven count
`count_primes_above_with_frobenius_eq_sigma`), and `N P = N рқ”ӯ` for degree-one `P`. -/
private theorem primeIdealZetaSum_fibre_eq_smul
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K))
    (ПғE : Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (hПғE : letI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
        (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
      ПғE.restrictScalars K = Пғ)
    [IsMulCommutative Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))]
    (horderE : orderOf Пғ
      = Nat.card Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    {s : в„қ} (hs : 1 < s) :
    haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
      (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
    primeIdealZetaSum
        {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
          P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P вҲ§
          frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
            = ConjClasses.mk ПғE вҲ§ (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1 вҲ§
          UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K))} s
      = ((Nat.card Gal(L/K) : в„қ) / (orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier))
        * primeIdealZetaSum {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ вҲ§
            frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = ConjClasses.mk Пғ} s := by
  classical
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
  haveI : IsGalois (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) L :=
    IsGalois.tower_top_intermediateField _
  set Sset := {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ вҲ§
    frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = ConjClasses.mk Пғ} with hSset
  set TвӮҒset := {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
    P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P вҲ§
    frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P = ConjClasses.mk ПғE вҲ§
    (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1 вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K))} with hTвӮҒset
  -- The two `primeIdealZetaSum` subtypes.
  set S' := {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) // рқ”ӯ вҲҲ Sset вҲ§ рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”ӯ вү  вҠҘ} with hS'
  -- Fibre projection `g : TвӮҒ' вҶ’ S'`, `P вҶҰ P вҲ© рқ“һ K`.
  have hgmem : вҲҖ P : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ},
      P.1.under (рқ“һ K) вҲҲ Sset вҲ§ (P.1.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime вҲ§ P.1.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := by
    rintro вҹЁP, вҹЁhPp, hPunr, hPfrob, hPdeg, hunrPвҹ©, _, hPbotвҹ©
    haveI := hPp
    refine вҹЁвҹЁinferInstance, hunrP, ?_вҹ©, inferInstance, UnramifiedIn.ne_bot K L hunrPвҹ©
    exact frobeniusClass_under_eq_of_mem_fibre Пғ ПғE hПғE horderE P hunrP hPunr hPfrob hPdeg hPbot
  set g : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} вҶ’ S' :=
    fun P => вҹЁP.1.under (рқ“һ K), hgmem Pвҹ© with hg
  -- For each `P вҲҲ TвӮҒ`, `N P = N (P вҲ© рқ“һ K)` (degree one).
  have hnormeq : вҲҖ P : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ},
      (Ideal.absNorm P.1 : в„қ) = (Ideal.absNorm (P.1.under (рқ“һ K)) : в„қ) := by
    rintro вҹЁP, вҹЁhPp, _, _, hPdeg, _вҹ©, _, hPbotвҹ©
    haveI := hPp
    haveI : (P.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime := inferInstance
    have hpbot : P.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := Ideal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot (рқ“һ K) hPbot
    haveI : P.LiesOver (P.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := P)
    have hpow := Ideal.absNorm_eq_pow_inertiaDeg_of_liesOver P (P.under (рқ“һ K)) inferInstance hpbot
    rw [hPdeg, pow_one] at hpow
    rw [hpow]
  -- the fibre over `рқ”ӯ вҲҲ S` is finite with exactly `c := |G|/(fВ·|C|)` elements.
  have hcardfib : вҲҖ рқ”ӯ : S', (orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier) *
      Nat.card {P : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} // g P = рқ”ӯ} = Nat.card Gal(L/K) := by
    intro рқ”ӯ
    obtain вҹЁhpрқ”ӯ, hunrрқ”ӯ, hfrobрқ”ӯвҹ© := рқ”ӯ.2.1
    haveI := hpрқ”ӯ
    -- reindex the `g`-fibre to `card_fibre`'s `E`-prime fibre set.
    have hreindex : Nat.card {P : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} // g P = рқ”ӯ}
        = Nat.card {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) //
            P вҲҲ {P | P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))
                  L P вҲ§ frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
                  = ConjClasses.mk ПғE вҲ§ (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1}
              вҲ§ P.LiesOver рқ”ӯ.1 вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} := by
      refine Nat.card_congr вҹЁfun x => вҹЁx.1.1, ?_, ?_, x.1.2.2.2вҹ©,
        fun y => вҹЁвҹЁy.1, ?_, y.2.1.1, y.2.2.2вҹ©, ?_вҹ©, fun _ => rfl, fun _ => rflвҹ©
      В· exact вҹЁx.1.2.1.1, x.1.2.1.2.1, x.1.2.1.2.2.1, x.1.2.1.2.2.2.1вҹ©
      В· -- `P.LiesOver рқ”ӯ` from `g x = рқ”ӯ` (i.e. `P вҲ© рқ“һ K = рқ”ӯ`).
        exact вҹЁ(congrArg Subtype.val x.2).symm в–ё (Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := x.1.1)).overвҹ©
      В· -- membership in `TвӮҒset` from `card_fibre`-set + `P.LiesOver рқ”ӯ` (gives unramified-`K`).
        haveI := y.2.1.1
        have hunderK : y.1.under (рқ“һ K) = рқ”ӯ.1 := (y.2.2.1).over.symm
        exact вҹЁy.2.1.1, y.2.1.2.1, y.2.1.2.2.1, y.2.1.2.2.2, by rw [hunderK]; exact hunrрқ”ӯвҹ©
      В· -- `g y = рқ”ӯ`
        exact Subtype.ext (y.2.2.1).over.symm
    rw [hreindex, card_fibre_E_eq_card_fibre_L Пғ ПғE hПғE horderE рқ”ӯ.1 hunrрқ”ӯ hfrobрқ”ӯ]
    rw [show orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier
        * Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ.1) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
          frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrрқ”ӯ рқ”“ hP) = Пғ}
        = Nat.card {рқ”“ : Ideal (рқ“һ L) // вҲғ (_ : рқ”“.IsPrime) (hP : рқ”“.LiesOver рқ”ӯ.1) (_ : рқ”“ вү  вҠҘ),
          frobeniusAt K L рқ”“ (UnramifiedIn.ramificationIdx_eq_one K L hunrрқ”ӯ рқ”“ hP) = Пғ}
          * orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier from by ring]
    exact count_primes_above_with_frobenius_eq_sigma K L Пғ (ConjClasses.mk Пғ) rfl рқ”ӯ.1 hunrрқ”ӯ hfrobрқ”ӯ
  -- each fibre is finite (the `E`-primes above `рқ”ӯ` form a finite set).
  have hfibfin : вҲҖ рқ”ӯ : S', Finite {P : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} // g P = рқ”ӯ} := by
    intro рқ”ӯ
    haveI := рқ”ӯ.2.2.1
    haveI : рқ”ӯ.1.IsMaximal := рқ”ӯ.2.2.1.isMaximal рқ”ӯ.2.2.2
    haveI : Finite (рқ”ӯ.1.primesOver
        (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :=
      (IsDedekindDomain.primesOver_finite рқ”ӯ.1 _).to_subtype
    refine Finite.of_injective (ОІ := рқ”ӯ.1.primesOver
        (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
      (fun P => вҹЁP.1.1, P.1.2.2.1, ?_вҹ©) ?_
    В· haveI := P.1.2.2.1
      exact вҹЁ(congrArg Subtype.val P.2).symm в–ё (Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := P.1.1)).overвҹ©
    В· rintro вҹЁвҹЁP, hPвҹ©, hgPвҹ© вҹЁвҹЁQ, hQвҹ©, hgQвҹ© hPQ
      simpa using hPQ
  -- the constant fibre value `c = |G|/(fВ·|C|)`.
  have hordC_pos : (0 : в„қ) < orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier := by
    have hвӮҒ : 0 < orderOf Пғ := by rw [orderOf_pos_iff]; exact isOfFinOrder_of_finite Пғ
    have hвӮӮ : 0 < Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier := by
      have : Nonempty (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier := вҹЁвҹЁПғ, ConjClasses.mem_carrier_mkвҹ©вҹ©
      exact Nat.card_pos
    positivity
  rw [primeIdealZetaSum_def, primeIdealZetaSum_def]
  -- the summand `N PвҒ»Лў = (h вҲҳ g) P` with `h рқ”ӯ = N рқ”ӯвҒ»Лў`; group over the `K`-prime fibre.
  set h : S' вҶ’ в„қ := fun рқ”ӯ => (Ideal.absNorm рқ”ӯ.1 : в„қ) ^ (-s) with hh
  have hFsumm : Summable (fun P : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} => h (g P)) :=
    (summable_prime_absNorm_rpow TвӮҒset hs).congr fun P => congrArg (В· ^ (-s)) (hnormeq P)
  -- rewrite the `TвӮҒ`-summand `N PвҒ»Лў` to `(h вҲҳ g) P = N (P вҲ© рқ“һ K)вҒ»Лў`.
  rw [tsum_congr (fun P => congrArg (В· ^ (-s)) (hnormeq P)),
    show (fun P : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} =>
      (Ideal.absNorm (P.1.under (рқ“һ K)) : в„қ) ^ (-s)) = (fun P => h (g P)) from rfl,
    (hFsumm.hasSum.tsum_fiberwise g).tsum_eq.symm]
  -- inner sum over each fibre: constant `h рқ”ӯ`, finite fibre with `c` elements.
  have hequivfib : вҲҖ рқ”ӯ : S', (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set _) вүғ
      {P : {P // P вҲҲ TвӮҒset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} // g P = рқ”ӯ} :=
    fun рқ”ӯ => Equiv.subtypeEquivRight fun _ => Iff.rfl
  have hinner : вҲҖ рқ”ӯ : S', вҲ‘' P : (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set _), h (g P)
      = ((Nat.card Gal(L/K) : в„қ) / (orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier)) * h рқ”ӯ := by
    intro рқ”ӯ
    haveI := hfibfin рқ”ӯ
    haveI : Finite (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set _) := Finite.of_equiv _ (hequivfib рқ”ӯ).symm
    letI := Fintype.ofFinite (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set _)
    have hval : вҲҖ P : (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set _), h (g P.1) = h рқ”ӯ := fun P => by
      rw [show g P.1 = рқ”ӯ from P.2]
    rw [tsum_congr hval, tsum_fintype, Finset.sum_const, Finset.card_univ,
      вҶҗ Nat.card_eq_fintype_card, nsmul_eq_mul]
    congr 1
    -- `(card fibre : в„қ) = |G|/(fВ·|C|)`, from `(fВ·|C|)В·card = |G|`.
    have hcard : (orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier) *
        Nat.card (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set _) = Nat.card Gal(L/K) := by
      rw [Nat.card_congr (hequivfib рқ”ӯ)]; exact hcardfib рқ”ӯ
    rw [eq_div_iff hordC_pos.ne', mul_comm]
    rw [вҶҗ hcard]; push_cast; ring
  rw [tsum_congr hinner, tsum_mul_left]

/-! ### Sub-lemmas for `primeIdealZetaSum_T2_div_univ_tendsto_zero` (LEAF B)

The complement `TвӮӮ = T вҲ– TвӮҒ` of degree-one primes splits into

* `A`: primes `P` of `рқ“һ E` whose underlying `K`-prime `рқ”ӯ = P вҲ© рқ“һ K` is unramified in `L` but
  whose inertia degree `f(P вҲЈ рқ”ӯ) вүҘ 2`, so `N P = Nрқ”ӯ^f вүҘ Nрқ”ӯВІ` and `N P^{-s} вүӨ Nрқ”ӯ^{-2}`; and
* `B`: primes `P` over one of the finitely many `K`-primes ramified in `L`.

The sum over `A` is bounded by `[E:K]В·ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯ^{-2}` (a fibre-counting argument: each `рқ”ӯ` has at
most `[E:K]` primes of `рқ“һ E` above it, by `Ideal.card_primesOverFinset_le_finrank`), and the sum
over `B` is bounded by the finite cardinality of `B`. Both are constants in `s`, so
`ОЈ_{TвӮӮ} s вүӨ C` for all `s > 1`, whence `ОЈ_{TвӮӮ}/ОЈ_univ^E вҶ’ 0` since `ОЈ_univ^E вҶ’ вҲһ`. -/

/-- **Fibre-counting bound for `в„қвүҘ0вҲһ`-valued sums.** If every fibre `g вҒ»В№' {y}` is finite with at
most `d` elements, then `ОЈ_b f(g b) вүӨ d В· ОЈ_y f y`: group `b` by its image `g b`, on each fibre
the summand is the constant `f y`, and the fibre has `вүӨ d` terms. -/
private theorem tsum_comp_le_card_fibre_mul {ОІ Оі : Type*} (g : ОІ вҶ’ Оі) (f : Оі вҶ’ в„қвүҘ0вҲһ) (d : в„•)
    (hfin : вҲҖ y, Finite (g вҒ»В№' {y} : Set ОІ))
    (hfib : вҲҖ y, Nat.card (g вҒ»В№' {y} : Set ОІ) вүӨ d) :
    вҲ‘' b, f (g b) вүӨ (d : в„қвүҘ0вҲһ) * вҲ‘' y, f y := by
  rw [вҶҗ ENNReal.tsum_fiberwise (fun b => f (g b)) g, вҶҗ ENNReal.tsum_mul_left]
  refine ENNReal.tsum_le_tsum (fun y => ?_)
  have hconst : вҲҖ b : (g вҒ»В№' {y} : Set ОІ), f (g b) = f y := fun b => by
    have hb : g b.1 = y := b.2
    rw [hb]
  rw [tsum_congr hconst]
  haveI := hfin y
  letI := Fintype.ofFinite (g вҒ»В№' {y} : Set ОІ)
  rw [tsum_fintype, Finset.sum_const, Finset.card_univ, вҶҗ Nat.card_eq_fintype_card, nsmul_eq_mul]
  have hcast : ((Nat.card (g вҒ»В№' {y} : Set ОІ) : в„•) : в„қвүҘ0вҲһ) вүӨ (d : в„қвүҘ0вҲһ) := by exact_mod_cast hfib y
  gcongr

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **The degree-`вүҘ 2` part of `TвӮӮ` is bounded by a constant.** For `1 < s`, the partial sum over
the set `A` of primes `P` of `рқ“һ E` whose underlying `K`-prime is unramified in `L` but of inertia
degree `вүҘ 2` is bounded by `[E:K]В·ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯ^{-2}`. Indeed `N P = Nрқ”ӯ^{f}` with `f вүҘ 2`
(`Ideal.absNorm_eq_pow_inertiaDeg_of_liesOver`), so `N P^{-s} вүӨ Nрқ”ӯ^{-2}` for `s вүҘ 1` and
`Nрқ”ӯ вүҘ 2`; grouping the `E`-primes by their `K`-prime fibre (each of size `вүӨ [E:K]` via
`Ideal.card_primesOverFinset_le_finrank`) gives the bound. -/
private theorem primeIdealZetaSum_degTwo_le [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) {s : в„қ}
    (hs : 1 < s) (Aset : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))))
    (hA : Aset = {P | P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ вҲ§
      UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K)) вҲ§ 2 вүӨ (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P}) :
    primeIdealZetaSum Aset s
      вүӨ (Module.finrank K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) : в„қ)
        * primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ K))) 2 := by
  classical
  letI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
  haveI : NoZeroSMulDivisors (рқ“һ K)
      (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) :=
    вҹЁfun {c x} h => by
      rw [Algebra.smul_def, mul_eq_zero] at h
      exact h.imp (fun h => RingOfIntegers.algebraMap.injective K _ (by rwa [map_zero])) idвҹ©
  set AP := {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) //
    P вҲҲ Aset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} with hAP
  set KP := {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) // рқ”ӯ вҲҲ (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ K))) вҲ§ рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”ӯ вү  вҠҘ} with hKP
  have hunder : вҲҖ P : AP, (P.1.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime вҲ§ P.1.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := by
    rintro вҹЁP, hPA, hPp, hPbвҹ©; haveI := hPp
    exact вҹЁinferInstance, Ideal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot (рқ“һ K) hPbвҹ©
  set g : AP вҶ’ KP := fun P => вҹЁP.1.under (рқ“һ K), mem_univ _, (hunder P).1, (hunder P).2вҹ© with hg
  set FA : AP вҶ’ в„қвүҘ0вҲһ := fun P => ENNReal.ofReal ((Ideal.absNorm P.1 : в„қ) ^ (-s)) with hFA
  set FK : KP вҶ’ в„қвүҘ0вҲһ := fun рқ”ӯ => ENNReal.ofReal ((Ideal.absNorm рқ”ӯ.1 : в„қ) ^ (-(2 : в„қ))) with hFK
  -- per-term: `N P^{-s} вүӨ N(P вҲ© рқ“һ K)^{-2}`.
  have hterm : вҲҖ P : AP, FA P вүӨ FK (g P) := by
    rintro вҹЁP, hPA, hPp, hPbвҹ©
    haveI := hPp
    rw [hA] at hPA
    obtain вҹЁ-, -, _, hdegвҹ© := hPA
    have hppr : (P.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime := inferInstance
    have hpbot : P.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := Ideal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot (рқ“һ K) hPb
    haveI : P.LiesOver (P.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := P)
    have hpow := Ideal.absNorm_eq_pow_inertiaDeg_of_liesOver P (P.under (рқ“һ K)) hppr hpbot
    have hn2 : 2 вүӨ Ideal.absNorm (P.under (рқ“һ K)) := by
      have h0 : Ideal.absNorm (P.under (рқ“һ K)) вү  0 := by
        rw [Ne, Ideal.absNorm_eq_zero_iff]; exact hpbot
      have h1 : Ideal.absNorm (P.under (рқ“һ K)) вү  1 := by
        rw [Ne, Ideal.absNorm_eq_one_iff]; exact hppr.ne_top
      omega
    change ENNReal.ofReal ((Ideal.absNorm P : в„қ) ^ (-s))
      вүӨ ENNReal.ofReal ((Ideal.absNorm (P.under (рқ“һ K)) : в„қ) ^ (-(2 : в„қ)))
    refine ENNReal.ofReal_le_ofReal ?_
    rw [hpow]
    set n := Ideal.absNorm (P.under (рқ“һ K))
    set f := (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P
    have hn1 : (1 : в„қ) вүӨ (n : в„қ) := by exact_mod_cast Nat.one_le_of_lt hn2
    have hnpos : (0 : в„қ) < (n : в„қ) := by positivity
    rw [Nat.cast_pow, вҶҗ Real.rpow_natCast (n : в„қ) f, вҶҗ Real.rpow_mul hnpos.le]
    refine Real.rpow_le_rpow_of_exponent_le hn1 ?_
    have hfs : (2 : в„қ) вүӨ (f : в„қ) * s := by
      calc (2 : в„қ) = 2 * 1 := by ring
        _ вүӨ (f : в„қ) * s := mul_le_mul (by exact_mod_cast hdeg) hs.le (by norm_num) (by positivity)
    nlinarith [hfs]
  -- each `K`-prime fibre is finite with `вүӨ [E:K]` primes of `рқ“һ E` above it.
  have hinj : вҲҖ рқ”ӯ : KP, Finite (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set AP) вҲ§
      Nat.card (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set AP)
        вүӨ Module.finrank K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) := by
    intro рқ”ӯ
    haveI := рқ”ӯ.2.2.1
    haveI : рқ”ӯ.1.IsMaximal := рқ”ӯ.2.2.1.isMaximal рқ”ӯ.2.2.2
    set PO := {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) //
      P.IsPrime вҲ§ P.LiesOver рқ”ӯ.1} with hPO
    have hmem : вҲҖ P : (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set AP), P.1.1.IsPrime вҲ§ P.1.1.LiesOver рқ”ӯ.1 := by
      rintro вҹЁвҹЁP, hPA, hPp, hPbвҹ©, hgPвҹ©
      haveI := hPp
      have hund : P.under (рқ“һ K) = рқ”ӯ.1 := congrArg Subtype.val hgP
      exact вҹЁhPp, вҹЁhund в–ё (Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := P)).overвҹ©вҹ©
    set hmap : (g вҒ»В№' {рқ”ӯ} : Set AP) вҶ’ PO := fun P => вҹЁP.1.1, hmem Pвҹ© with hhmap
    have hmapinj : Function.Injective hmap := by
      rintro вҹЁвҹЁP, hPвҹ©, hgPвҹ© вҹЁвҹЁQ, hQвҹ©, hgQвҹ© hPQ
      have hPeqQ : P = Q := congrArg Subtype.val hPQ
      exact Subtype.ext (Subtype.ext hPeqQ)
    haveI hPOfin : Finite PO :=
      (IsDedekindDomain.primesOver_finite рқ”ӯ.1
        (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))).to_subtype
    refine вҹЁFinite.of_injective hmap hmapinj, (Nat.card_le_card_of_injective hmap hmapinj).trans ?_вҹ©
    have hcard : Nat.card PO
        = (IsDedekindDomain.primesOverFinset рқ”ӯ.1
            (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))).card := by
      rw [show PO = вҶҘ(рқ”ӯ.1.primesOver
          (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) from rfl,
        Nat.card_coe_set_eq, вҶҗ IsDedekindDomain.coe_primesOverFinset рқ”ӯ.2.2.2,
        Set.ncard_coe_finset]
    rw [hcard]
    exact Ideal.card_primesOverFinset_le_finrank (R := рқ“һ K)
      (S := рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))
      (K := K) (L := вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) рқ”ӯ.2.2.2
  -- convert both sums to `в„қвүҘ0вҲһ` and chain the bounds.
  have hsummA : Summable (fun P : AP => (Ideal.absNorm P.1 : в„қ) ^ (-s)) :=
    summable_prime_absNorm_rpow Aset (by linarith)
  have hsummK : Summable (fun рқ”ӯ : KP => (Ideal.absNorm рқ”ӯ.1 : в„қ) ^ (-(2 : в„қ))) :=
    summable_prime_absNorm_rpow (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ K))) (by norm_num)
  have hnonnegA : вҲҖ P : AP, 0 вүӨ (Ideal.absNorm P.1 : в„қ) ^ (-s) := fun P => by positivity
  have hnonnegK : вҲҖ рқ”ӯ : KP, 0 вүӨ (Ideal.absNorm рқ”ӯ.1 : в„қ) ^ (-(2 : в„қ)) := fun рқ”ӯ => by positivity
  have hAreal : primeIdealZetaSum Aset s = (вҲ‘' P : AP, FA P).toReal := by
    rw [primeIdealZetaSum_def, hFA, вҶҗ ENNReal.ofReal_tsum_of_nonneg hnonnegA hsummA,
      ENNReal.toReal_ofReal (tsum_nonneg hnonnegA)]
  have hKreal : primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ K))) 2 = (вҲ‘' рқ”ӯ : KP, FK рқ”ӯ).toReal := by
    rw [primeIdealZetaSum_def, hFK, вҶҗ ENNReal.ofReal_tsum_of_nonneg hnonnegK hsummK,
      ENNReal.toReal_ofReal (tsum_nonneg hnonnegK)]
  have hchain : вҲ‘' P : AP, FA P
      вүӨ (Module.finrank K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) : в„қвүҘ0вҲһ)
        * вҲ‘' рқ”ӯ : KP, FK рқ”ӯ :=
    calc вҲ‘' P : AP, FA P вүӨ вҲ‘' P : AP, FK (g P) := ENNReal.tsum_le_tsum hterm
      _ вүӨ (Module.finrank K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) : в„қвүҘ0вҲһ)
            * вҲ‘' рқ”ӯ : KP, FK рқ”ӯ :=
          tsum_comp_le_card_fibre_mul g FK _ (fun рқ”ӯ => (hinj рқ”ӯ).1) (fun рқ”ӯ => (hinj рқ”ӯ).2)
  rw [hAreal, hKreal]
  have hfin : вҲ‘' рқ”ӯ : KP, FK рқ”ӯ вү  вҲһ := by
    rw [hFK, вҶҗ ENNReal.ofReal_tsum_of_nonneg hnonnegK hsummK]; exact ENNReal.ofReal_ne_top
  have hbtop : (Module.finrank K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) : в„қвүҘ0вҲһ)
      * вҲ‘' рқ”ӯ : KP, FK рқ”ӯ вү  вҲһ := ENNReal.mul_ne_top (by simp) hfin
  refine le_of_le_of_eq (ENNReal.toReal_mono hbtop hchain) ?_
  rw [ENNReal.toReal_mul, ENNReal.toReal_natCast]

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **The ramified part of `TвӮӮ` is a finite set.** The primes `P` of `рқ“һ E` whose underlying
`K`-prime is ramified in `L` lie over one of the finitely many ramified `K`-primes
(`finite_ramifiedIn`), and each `K`-prime has finitely many primes of `рқ“һ E` above it
(`IsDedekindDomain.primesOver_finite`); hence the set is finite. -/
private theorem ramifiedBelow_finite [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K))
    (Bset : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))))
    (hB : Bset = {P | P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ вҲ§ В¬ UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K))}) :
    Bset.Finite := by
  classical
  have hram : {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ рқ”ӯ вү  вҠҘ вҲ§ В¬ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ}.Finite :=
    finite_ramifiedIn K L
  apply Set.Finite.subset (hram.biUnion (t := fun рқ”ӯ =>
    (рқ”ӯ.primesOver (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))) ?_)
  В· rw [hB]
    rintro P вҹЁhPp, hPb, hPnuвҹ©
    haveI := hPp
    have hppr : (P.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime := inferInstance
    have hpbot : P.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := Ideal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot (рқ“һ K) hPb
    exact Set.mem_biUnion вҹЁhppr, hpbot, hPnuвҹ©
      вҹЁhPp, Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := P)вҹ©
  В· rintro рқ”ӯ вҹЁhp, hb, -вҹ©
    haveI := hp
    haveI : рқ”ӯ.IsMaximal := hp.isMaximal hb
    exact IsDedekindDomain.primesOver_finite рқ”ӯ _

open scoped Pointwise in
/-- **LEAF B: the degree-`вүҘ 2` part of `T` vanishes in the density ratio** (Sharifi 7.2.2
p. 143, "`ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯвҒ»Лў ~ ОЈ_P NPвҒ»Лў`"). The complement `TвӮӮ = T вҲ– TвӮҒ` consists of primes `P` of `рқ“һ E`
that are either of inertia degree `вүҘ 2` over `K` (so `N P = N(P вҲ© рқ“һ K)^{вүҘ2}`, contributing a
`Оҳ(ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯвҒ»ВІЛў)` tail that is bounded near `s = 1`) or lie over one of the finitely many primes
of `рқ“һ K` ramified in `L` (a finite contribution).  Both are `o(ОЈ_univ^E)` since
`ОЈ_univ^E вҶ’ вҲһ`, so `ОЈ_{TвӮӮ}/ОЈ_univ^E вҶ’ 0`.

This is the asymptotic content that the (false) exact identity
`ОЈ_S = (f|C|/|G|)В·ОЈ_T` elided: the relation `ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯвҒ»Лў ~ ОЈ_P NPвҒ»Лў` holds only in the
`s вҶ’ 1вҒә` limit, with the higher-degree primes of `E` over `K` forming the discrepancy. -/
private theorem primeIdealZetaSum_T2_div_univ_tendsto_zero
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K))
    (ПғE : Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
    (TвӮӮset : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))))
    (hTвӮӮ : TвӮӮset = {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
        P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P вҲ§
        frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
          = ConjClasses.mk ПғE} \
      {P вҲҲ {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
          P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P вҲ§
          frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
            = ConjClasses.mk ПғE} |
        (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1 вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K))}) :
    Tendsto (fun s : в„қ вҶҰ primeIdealZetaSum TвӮӮset s
      / primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField
        (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))) s) (рқ“қ[>] 1) (рқ“қ 0) := by
  haveI : IsGalois вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    IsGalois.tower_top_intermediateField _
  -- `TвӮӮ вҠҶ A вҲӘ B` (disjoint): `A` = unramified-below but inertia degree `вүҘ 2`; `B` = ramified below.
  set Aset := {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
    P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K)) вҲ§
    2 вүӨ (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P} with hAdef
  set Bset := {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
    P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ вҲ§ В¬ UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K))} with hBdef
  have hsub : TвӮӮset вҠҶ Aset вҲӘ Bset := by
    rw [hTвӮӮ]
    rintro P вҹЁвҹЁhPp, hPunr, hPfrвҹ©, hPnotT1вҹ©
    haveI := hPp
    simp only [Set.mem_setOf_eq, not_and] at hPnotT1
    have hPb : P вү  вҠҘ := UnramifiedIn.ne_bot _ L hPunr
    by_cases hunrK : UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K))
    В· -- unramified below `K` but not degree one: inertia degree `вүҘ 2`.
      refine Or.inl вҹЁhPp, hPb, hunrK, ?_вҹ©
      have hdegne : (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P вү  1 := fun hdeg1 =>
        hPnotT1 вҹЁhPp, hPunr, hPfrвҹ© hdeg1 hunrK
      have hppr : (P.under (рқ“һ K)).IsPrime := inferInstance
      have hpbot : P.under (рқ“һ K) вү  вҠҘ := Ideal.IsIntegral.comap_ne_bot (рқ“һ K) hPb
      haveI : (P.under (рқ“һ K)).IsMaximal := hppr.isMaximal hpbot
      haveI : P.LiesOver (P.under (рқ“һ K)) := Ideal.over_under (A := рқ“һ K) (P := P)
      have hpos : 0 < (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P := Ideal.inertiaDeg_pos' _ _
      omega
    В· exact Or.inr вҹЁhPp, hPb, hunrKвҹ©
  have hdisj : Disjoint Aset Bset := by
    rw [Set.disjoint_left]
    rintro P вҹЁ-, -, hunrK, -вҹ© вҹЁ-, -, hnunrKвҹ©
    exact hnunrK hunrK
  have hBfin : Bset.Finite := ramifiedBelow_finite Пғ Bset hBdef
  -- the uniform constant `C = [E:K]В·ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯ^{-2} + |B|` bounding `ОЈ_{TвӮӮ} s` for all `s > 1`.
  refine tendsto_primeIdealZetaSum_div_univ_zero_of_le_const
    (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) TвӮӮset
    ((Module.finrank K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) : в„қ)
        * primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ K))) 2
      + (Nat.card {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) //
          P вҲҲ Bset вҲ§ P.IsPrime вҲ§ P вү  вҠҘ} : в„қ)) ?_
  filter_upwards [self_mem_nhdsWithin] with s hs
  simp only [Set.mem_Ioi] at hs
  calc primeIdealZetaSum TвӮӮset s вүӨ primeIdealZetaSum (Aset вҲӘ Bset) s :=
        primeIdealZetaSum_le_of_subset hsub hs
    _ = primeIdealZetaSum Aset s + primeIdealZetaSum Bset s :=
        primeIdealZetaSum_union_of_disjoint hdisj hs
    _ вүӨ _ := add_le_add (primeIdealZetaSum_degTwo_le Пғ hs Aset hAdef)
        (primeIdealZetaSum_le_card_of_finite
          (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) hBfin (by linarith))

/-- **Density-lift through the fixed-field subextension** (Sharifi 7.2.2
Step 1, p. 143). Let `Пғ вҲҲ Gal(L/K)`, `E = L^вҹЁПғвҹ©` the fixed field of the
cyclic subgroup `вҹЁПғвҹ©`, and `Пғ_E вҲҲ Gal(L/E)` the corresponding element.
Given the abelian-case density over `E` for the Frobenius-fibre of `Пғ_E`
(value `1/|Gal(L/E)|`), the density over `K` of the Frobenius **class** of
`Пғ` is `|C|/|G|`.

Source quote (verbatim, p. 143): "Оҙ(S) = вҖҰ = (f|C|/|G|) Оҙ(T_Пғ),
recalling once again that `ОЈ_рқ”ӯ Nрқ”ӯ^{-s} ~ ОЈ_P NP^{-s}`. Supposing the
theorem for K/E, we have Оҙ(T_Пғ) = 1/f, and we therefore obtain Оҙ(S) =
|C|/|G|." Here `f = ord Пғ = |Gal(L/E)|`, and the counting factor is
`count_primes_above_with_frobenius_eq_sigma`.

The hypothesis `hEfix` records that `E` is the fixed field of `вҹЁПғвҹ©`; the
hypothesis `hПғE` records that `Пғ_E` restricts to `Пғ` over `K` (so `Пғ_E`
generates `Gal(L/E)` and a prime with `Frob^E_рқ”“ = Пғ_E` has `Frob^K_рқ”“ = Пғ`);
the hypothesis `hab` is the abelian-case output for `L/E` from
`chebotarev_abelian`. -/
theorem density_lift_through_fixedField
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (Пғ : Gal(L/K)) (E : IntermediateField K L) (ПғE : Gal(L/E))
    (hПғE : letI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘE L := E.isScalarTower_mid'; ПғE.restrictScalars K = Пғ)
    (_hEfix : E = IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))
    (_hab : HasDirichletDensity
        {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘE) | P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘE L P вҲ§
          frobeniusClass вҶҘE L P = ConjClasses.mk ПғE}
        ((Nat.card Gal(L/E) : в„қ)вҒ»В№)) :
    HasDirichletDensity
      {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ вҲ§
        frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = ConjClasses.mk Пғ}
      ((Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier : в„қ) / Nat.card Gal(L/K)) := by
  subst _hEfix
  haveI : IsScalarTower K вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L :=
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).isScalarTower_mid'
  -- `f = ord Пғ = |Gal(L/E)|`.
  have horder : (Nat.card Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) : в„қ)
      = orderOf Пғ := by
    rw [вҶҗ Nat.card_congr (IntermediateField.subgroupEquivAlgEquiv (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).toEquiv,
      Nat.card_zpowers]
  -- `Gal(L/E)` is abelian (`E` is the fixed field of the cyclic `вҹЁПғвҹ©`).
  haveI : IsMulCommutative Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) :=
    .of_comm fun a b => by
      obtain вҹЁx, rflвҹ© := (IntermediateField.subgroupEquivAlgEquiv (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).surjective a
      obtain вҹЁy, rflвҹ© := (IntermediateField.subgroupEquivAlgEquiv (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).surjective b
      rw [вҶҗ map_mul _ x y, вҶҗ map_mul _ y x, mul_comm' x y]
  set Tset := {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
    P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P вҲ§
    frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P
      = ConjClasses.mk ПғE} with hTset
  set TвӮҒset := {P вҲҲ Tset | (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1 вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K))}
    with hTвӮҒset
  set TвӮӮset := Tset \ TвӮҒset with hTвӮӮset
  have horderE' : orderOf Пғ = Nat.card Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))
      := by
    rw [вҶҗ Nat.card_congr (IntermediateField.subgroupEquivAlgEquiv (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)).toEquiv,
      Nat.card_zpowers]
  -- `ОЈ_T = ОЈ_{TвӮҒ} + ОЈ_{TвӮӮ}` (disjoint union `T = TвӮҒ вҠ” TвӮӮ`).
  have hTвӮҒsub : TвӮҒset вҠҶ Tset := fun x hx => hx.1
  have hsplit : вҲҖ {s : в„қ}, 1 < s вҶ’ primeIdealZetaSum Tset s
      = primeIdealZetaSum TвӮҒset s + primeIdealZetaSum TвӮӮset s := by
    intro s hs
    have : Tset = TвӮҒset вҲӘ TвӮӮset := (Set.union_diff_cancel hTвӮҒsub).symm
    rw [this, primeIdealZetaSum_union_of_disjoint (Set.disjoint_sdiff_right) hs]
  -- `ОЈ_{TвӮӮ}/ОЈ_univ^E вҶ’ 0` (LEAF B): the degree-`вүҘ 2` (over `K`) primes of `T` contribute a
  -- `Оҳ(ОЈ Nрқ”ӯвҒ»ВІЛў)` tail (bounded near `s = 1`), and the primes over the finitely many ramified
  -- `рқ”ӯ` contribute a finite sum; both vanish against `ОЈ_univ^E вҶ’ вҲһ`.
  have hleafB : Tendsto (fun s : в„қ вҶҰ primeIdealZetaSum TвӮӮset s
      / primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField
        (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))) s) (рқ“қ[>] 1) (рқ“қ 0) :=
    primeIdealZetaSum_T2_div_univ_tendsto_zero Пғ ПғE TвӮӮset hTвӮӮset
  -- `ОЈ_{TвӮҒ}/ОЈ_univ^E вҶ’ 1/f` (`hab` minus the vanishing tail).
  have htendTвӮҒ : Tendsto (fun s : в„қ вҶҰ primeIdealZetaSum TвӮҒset s
      / primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField
        (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))) s) (рқ“қ[>] 1)
      (рқ“қ ((Nat.card Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) : в„қ)вҒ»В№)) := by
    have := (_hab.sub hleafB)
    rw [sub_zero] at this
    refine this.congr' ?_
    filter_upwards [self_mem_nhdsWithin] with s hs
    simp only [mem_Ioi] at hs
    rw [hsplit hs]; ring
  rw [HasDirichletDensity]
  -- `Оҙ_K(S) = (f|C|/|G|)В·(ОЈ_{TвӮҒ}/ОЈ_univ^E)В·(ОЈ_univ^E/ОЈ_univ^K)`.
  have hmain : Tendsto
      (fun s : в„қ вҶҰ ((orderOf Пғ : в„қ) * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier / Nat.card Gal(L/K))
        * (primeIdealZetaSum TвӮҒset s
              / primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField
                (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))) s)
          * (primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField
              (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))))) s
              / primeIdealZetaSum (univ : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ K))) s))
      (рқ“қ[>] 1)
      (рқ“қ (((orderOf Пғ : в„қ) * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier / Nat.card Gal(L/K))
        * (Nat.card Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) : в„қ)вҒ»В№ * 1)) :=
    ((htendTвӮҒ.const_mul _).mul (univ_ratio_E_K_tendsto_one _))
  have hval : ((orderOf Пғ : в„қ) * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier / Nat.card Gal(L/K))
        * (Nat.card Gal(L/(вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))) : в„қ)вҒ»В№ * 1
      = (Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier : в„қ) / Nat.card Gal(L/K) := by
    have hordne : (orderOf Пғ : в„қ) вү  0 := by
      have : 0 < orderOf Пғ := by rw [orderOf_pos_iff]; exact isOfFinOrder_of_finite Пғ
      positivity
    rw [horder, mul_one]
    field_simp
  rw [hval] at hmain
  refine hmain.congr' ?_
  filter_upwards [self_mem_nhdsWithin,
    (primeIdealZetaSum_univ_tendsto_atTop (вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField
      (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)))).eventually_gt_atTop 0] with s hs hEpos
  simp only [mem_Ioi] at hs
  -- LEAF A (`TвӮҒset` flattened): `ОЈ_{TвӮҒ} = (|G|/(f|C|))В·ОЈ_S`.
  have hTвӮҒflat : TвӮҒset = {P : Ideal (рқ“һ вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) |
      P.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P вҲ§
      frobeniusClass вҶҘ(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)) L P = ConjClasses.mk ПғE вҲ§
      (P.under (рқ“һ K)).inertiaDeg P = 1 вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L (P.under (рқ“һ K))} := by
    rw [hTвӮҒset, hTset]; ext P; simp only [Set.mem_setOf_eq]; tauto
  have hleafA := primeIdealZetaSum_fibre_eq_smul Пғ ПғE hПғE horderE' hs
  rw [вҶҗ hTвӮҒflat] at hleafA
  have hc_pos : (0 : в„қ) < orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier := by
    have hвӮҒ : 0 < orderOf Пғ := by rw [orderOf_pos_iff]; exact isOfFinOrder_of_finite Пғ
    have hвӮӮ : 0 < Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier := by
      have : Nonempty (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier := вҹЁвҹЁПғ, ConjClasses.mem_carrier_mkвҹ©вҹ©
      exact Nat.card_pos
    positivity
  have hG_pos : (0 : в„қ) < Nat.card Gal(L/K) := by exact_mod_cast Nat.card_pos
  -- `ОЈ_S = (f|C|/|G|)В·ОЈ_{TвӮҒ}`; the rest cancels `ОЈ_univ^E`.
  have hAB : ((orderOf Пғ : в„қ) * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier / Nat.card Gal(L/K))
      * ((Nat.card Gal(L/K) : в„қ) / (orderOf Пғ * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier)) = 1 := by
    rw [div_mul_div_comm, mul_comm ((orderOf Пғ : в„қ) * _), div_self (by positivity)]
  have hSeq : primeIdealZetaSum {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ вҲ§
        frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = ConjClasses.mk Пғ} s
      = ((orderOf Пғ : в„қ) * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier / Nat.card Gal(L/K))
        * primeIdealZetaSum TвӮҒset s := by
    rw [hleafA, вҶҗ mul_assoc, hAB, one_mul]
  rw [hSeq, mul_assoc ((orderOf Пғ : в„қ) * Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk Пғ).carrier / Nat.card Gal(L/K)),
    div_mul_div_cancelвӮҖ hEpos.ne']
  ring

/-- **Chebotarev's density theorem** (Sharifi 7.2.2; SL Appendix).

For a finite Galois extension `L/K` of number fields with Galois group `G`
and a conjugacy class `C вҠҶ G`, the Dirichlet density of the set of primes
`рқ”ӯ` of `рқ“һ K` (unramified in `L`) such that the Frobenius conjugacy class of
`рқ”ӯ` is `C` equals `|C| / |G|`. -/
theorem chebotarev_density
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (C : ConjClasses Gal(L/K)) :
    HasDirichletDensity
      {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ вҲ§
        frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = C}
      ((Nat.card C.carrier : в„қ) / Nat.card Gal(L/K)) := by
  obtain вҹЁПғ, rflвҹ© := ConjClasses.mk_surjective C
  let e := IntermediateField.subgroupEquivAlgEquiv (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ)
  have : IsMulCommutative Gal(L/(IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))) :=
    .of_comm fun a b => by
      obtain вҹЁx, rflвҹ© := e.surjective a
      obtain вҹЁy, rflвҹ© := e.surjective b
      rw [вҶҗ map_mul e x y, вҶҗ map_mul e y x, mul_comm' x y]
  exact density_lift_through_fixedField Пғ
    (IntermediateField.fixedField (Subgroup.zpowers Пғ))
    (e вҹЁПғ, Subgroup.mem_zpowers Пғвҹ©) (by ext x; rfl) rfl
    (chebotarev_abelian _ L (e вҹЁПғ, Subgroup.mem_zpowers Пғвҹ©))

/-- In a commutative finite group every conjugacy class is a singleton,
so `|C| = 1`. -/
theorem ConjClasses_carrier_card_eq_one_of_comm
    {G : Type*} [Group G] [IsMulCommutative G] [Finite G] (g : G) :
    Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk g).carrier = 1 := by
  letI : CommMonoid G := IsMulCommutative.instCommMonoid
  have h : (ConjClasses.mk g).carrier = {g} := by
    ext a
    simp [ConjClasses.mem_carrier_iff_mk_eq, ConjClasses.mk_eq_mk_iff_isConj, isConj_iff_eq]
  rw [h, Nat.card_coe_set_eq, Set.ncard_singleton]

/-- **Chebotarev's density theorem, abelian case.** For an abelian Galois
extension `L/K`, the Dirichlet density of primes `рқ”ӯ` of `рқ“һ K` unramified in
`L` whose Frobenius conjugacy class is `C` is `|C| / |Gal(L/K)|`. -/
theorem chebotarev_density_of_comm
    [FiniteDimensional K L] [IsMulCommutative Gal(L/K)] (C : ConjClasses Gal(L/K)) :
    HasDirichletDensity
      {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ вҲ§
        frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = C}
      ((Nat.card C.carrier : в„қ) / Nat.card Gal(L/K)) := by
  obtain вҹЁПғ, rflвҹ© := ConjClasses.mk_surjective C
  simpa [ConjClasses_carrier_card_eq_one_of_comm Пғ] using chebotarev_abelian K L Пғ

/-- Sub-lemma: a set of prime ideals with positive Dirichlet density is
infinite. Contrapositive: a finite set has density `0` (by
`hasDirichletDensity_of_finite` from `Density.lean`). -/
theorem infinite_of_hasDirichletDensity_pos
    {S : Set (Ideal (рқ“һ K))} {Оҙ : в„қ} (h : HasDirichletDensity S Оҙ) (hОҙ : 0 < Оҙ) :
    S.Infinite :=
  fun hfin вҶҰ hОҙ.ne' (tendsto_nhds_unique h (hasDirichletDensity_of_finite K hfin))

/-- The carrier of a conjugacy class in a finite group has positive cardinality. -/
theorem ConjClasses_carrier_card_pos
    {G : Type*} [Group G] [Finite G] (C : ConjClasses G) :
    0 < Nat.card C.carrier := by
  obtain вҹЁa, rflвҹ© := ConjClasses.mk_surjective C
  have : Nonempty (ConjClasses.mk a).carrier := вҹЁвҹЁa, ConjClasses.mem_carrier_mkвҹ©вҹ©
  exact Nat.card_pos

/-- Existence of *infinitely many* primes with each Frobenius conjugacy class
вҖ” a qualitative corollary of `chebotarev_density`. -/
theorem infinite_setOf_frobenius_class
    [FiniteDimensional K L] (C : ConjClasses Gal(L/K)) :
    Set.Infinite
      {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ вҲ§
        frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = C} := by
  refine infinite_of_hasDirichletDensity_pos (chebotarev_density C) ?_
  apply div_pos
  В· exact_mod_cast ConjClasses_carrier_card_pos C
  В· exact_mod_cast Nat.card_pos (Оұ := Gal(L/K))

/-- The identity conjugacy class in a finite group has carrier of cardinality `1`. -/
theorem ConjClasses_mk_one_carrier_card_eq_one
    (G : Type*) [Group G] [Finite G] :
    Nat.card (ConjClasses.mk (1 : G)).carrier = 1 := by
  have h : (ConjClasses.mk (1 : G)).carrier = {1} := by
    simp [Set.ext_iff, ConjClasses.mem_carrier_iff_mk_eq, ConjClasses.mk_eq_mk_iff_isConj]
  rw [h, Nat.card_coe_set_eq, Set.ncard_singleton]

/-- **Density of completely split primes** (Sharifi 7.1.14, as a corollary of
Chebotarev applied to the identity conjugacy class).

The Dirichlet density of primes `рқ”ӯ` of `рқ“һ K` that split completely in `L`
equals `1 / [L : K]`. -/
theorem density_split_completely :
    HasDirichletDensity
      {рқ”ӯ : Ideal (рқ“һ K) | рқ”ӯ.IsPrime вҲ§ UnramifiedIn K L рқ”ӯ вҲ§
        frobeniusClass K L рқ”ӯ = ConjClasses.mk 1}
      ((Module.finrank K L : в„қ)вҒ»В№) := by
  have h := chebotarev_density (ConjClasses.mk (1 : Gal(L/K)))
  rw [ConjClasses_mk_one_carrier_card_eq_one Gal(L/K), IsGalois.card_aut_eq_finrank K L] at h
  simpa using h

/-- **Dirichlet's theorem on primes in arithmetic progressions**, as a
density refinement of `Nat.infinite_setOf_prime_and_eq_mod`.

For coprime integers `a, n` with `1 вүӨ n` and `gcd a n = 1`, the Dirichlet
density of primes `p` with `p вүЎ a mod n` equals `1 / ПҶ(n)`. This is the
specialisation of Chebotarev to `K = в„ҡ`, `L = в„ҡ(Ој_n)` (Sharifi 7.2.3). -/
theorem dirichlet_primes_in_AP (n : в„•) (hn : 1 вүӨ n) (a : ZMod n) (ha : IsUnit a) :
    HasDirichletDensity
      ((fun p : в„• вҶҰ Ideal.span {(p : рқ“һ в„ҡ)}) ''
        {p : в„• | p.Prime вҲ§ (p : ZMod n) = a})
      ((Nat.totient n : в„қ)вҒ»В№) := by
  sorry

end Chebotarev
